ndex":84,"end_time":444,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":442.76,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Can you share what''s the responses we got?","index":85,"end_time":446.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":444,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, looks like there''s one here that I''ve pulled up.","index":86,"end_time":451.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":446.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you see them also?","index":87,"end_time":453.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":452.84,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, because.","index":88,"end_time":455.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":454.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And you guys have access to heyreach too.","index":89,"end_time":456.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":455.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can send that login over again if you guys want to log in this way.","index":90,"end_time":459.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":456.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, I haven''t checked.","index":91,"end_time":461.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":459.92,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":92,"end_time":461.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":461.04,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"But yeah, it looks like a conversation''s.","index":93,"end_time":463.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":462.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Been going on here for some time.","index":94,"end_time":465.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":463.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So set.","index":95,"end_time":468.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":467.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That takes one or two days for them to get through resumes.","index":96,"end_time":471.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":468.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Didn''t we change that from the resume?","index":97,"end_time":473.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":472.19,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Isn''t that so this is from November 29th.","index":98,"end_tim