gn.","index":113,"end_time":507.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":506.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m not sure I''m sending out messages for the new one yet either.","index":114,"end_time":511.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":507.88,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Yeah, they''re going out here.","index":115,"end_time":513.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":512.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you got new connections or.","index":116,"end_time":516.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":515,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, I always have so many.","index":117,"end_time":519.8,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":518.28,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Amy, what''s the latest with Amy?","index":118,"end_time":523.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":521.74,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Is there any follow up or anything?","index":119,"end_time":524.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":523.14,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Or nothing really.","index":120,"end_time":525.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":524.7,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Well, I just saw that message now.","index":121,"end_time":530.86,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":529.02,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"It came through like yesterday evening and.","index":122,"end_time":535.66,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":531.58,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Not really.","index":123,"end_time":539.74,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":539.02,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"I mean they have a commercially sold licensing.","index":124,"end_time":542.38,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":539.82,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"They have a SaaS tool to do this they built internally.","index":125,"end_time":545.9,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":542.7,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"I don''t think there''s much to do there.","index":126,"end_time":549.05,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":547.73,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Right.","index":127,"end_time":549.41