":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":142,"end_time":584.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":584.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Where''s the.","index":143,"end_time":585.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":585.02,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"What if I have a private.","index":144,"end_time":593.02,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":591.98,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"I don''t have any private conversations on LinkedIn but if I do they also go to this tool.","index":145,"end_time":597.74,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":593.1,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"So that was an option when you connected your profile.","index":146,"end_time":601.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":599.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"When I sent over like you can.","index":147,"end_time":602.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":601.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Do that through the extension it said.","index":148,"end_time":604.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":602.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Do you want all conversations or just.","index":149,"end_time":606.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":604.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"One started from Hayreach?","index":150,"end_time":607.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":606.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m not sure which one you selected.","index":151,"end_time":608.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":607.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m pretty sure it''s just the hay reach.","index":152,"end_time":610.87,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":609.27,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":153,"end_time":611.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":611.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":154,"end_time":612.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":611.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So Axel, that''s the new sequence that you guys had provided feedback on.","index":155,"end_time":616.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":612.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So there''s personalization or there''s a fallback message.","index":156,"end_time":620.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":618.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If it''s not able to provide that.","index":157,"end_time":622.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":620.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":158,"end_time":623.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":622.95,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I have to look at it again.","index":159,"end_time":625.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":624.47,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"It has been a while.","index":160,"end_time":626.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":625.55,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":161,"end_time":627.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":626.47,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":162,"end_time":629.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":628.98,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":163,"end_time":632.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":632.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I know Eli, Yumi and Hendrick have been go back and forth.","index":164,"end_time":637.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":632.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Looks like some screen recordings are being created.","index":165,"end_time":639.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":637.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I watched the two that you sent over.","index":166,"end_time":640.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":639.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Those are.","index":167,"end_time":643.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":643.219,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Those are fine for.","index":168,"end_time":644.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":643.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know what we need.","index":169,"end_time":645.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":644.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We just really need to see like.","index":170,"end_time":646.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":645.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What the.","index":171,"end_time":647.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":646.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"AI part looks like.","index":172,"end_time":650.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":648.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I know, Axel, we went through that on one of our calls as well.","index":173,"end_time":652.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":650.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then.","index":174,"end_time":654.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":653.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Can you share that, Eli, is that I haven''t seen it yet or have you shared it somewhere?","index":175,"end_time":657.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":654.22,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":176,"end_time":658.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":658.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I put it in the new north.","index":177,"end_time":662.3,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":660.94,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"I put it as I put in the chat.","index":178,"end_time":665.02,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":663.18,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"I put it in the SharePoint and I linked it in the chat.","index":179,"end_time":668.38,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":665.26,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Okay, I can check that.","index":180,"end_time":669.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":668.7,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I haven''t looked at it yet.","index":181,"end_time":670.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":669.86,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, they''re nothing too special.","index":182,"end_time":672.62,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":670.78,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"But I just kind of had a quick conversation with the AI.","index":183,"end_time":675.66,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":672.7,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Showed the resource plans and things like that.","index":184,"end_time":680.06,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":677.34,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"I actually was trying to meet with you, I think to review this.","index":185,"end_time":683.75,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":680.06,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Yeah, that is.","index":186,"end_time":688.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":687.51,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"That''s very beta, so I''m not sure what.","index":187,"end_time":690.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":688.31,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, I said we can make it look like it works, but it doesn''t if you.","index":188,"end_time":695.35,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":691.51,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"A lot of the times I tried to ask questions.","index":189,"end_time":698.869,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":695.75,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Yeah, we''re going to answer this.","index":190,"end_time":702.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":699.67,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So if you want to let me know some prompts and responses, we can just customize those.","index":191,"end_time":708.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":703.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This one works pretty well, right?","index":192,"end_time":710.64,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":709.24,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"But like it''s a little unmet.","index":193,"end_time":712.28,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":710.64,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"No, this is just linking to documentation.","index":194,"end_time":716.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":714.36,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"What it can do is help.","index":195,"end_time":717.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":716.68,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So currently it''s mostly around profiles helping you to fill out your profile.","index":196,"end_time":722.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":717.88,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So you can ask like make suggestions to improve my profile or something.","index":197,"end_time":726.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":722.12,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So it actually has some.","index":198,"end_time":728.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":727,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"It has some suggestions that you can do, but I. Yeah, I can look.","index":199,"end_time":732.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":729.64,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Look at it and give you some.","index":200,"end_time":734.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":733,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, this is not gonna.","index":201,"end_time":737.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":734.72,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"This is not gonna work.","index":202,"end_time":738.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":737.2,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"You have to know what its capabilities.","index":203,"end_time":739.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":738.04,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Actually it''s making suggestions when you first open these.","index":204,"end_time":742.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":740,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"These both kind of worked.","index":205,"end_time":744.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":742.6,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"I mean it didn''t tell us, but it did tell me where I could find this information.","index":206,"end_time":747.68,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":744.12,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s going to the documentation, but it''s not.","index":207,"end_time":750.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":747.92,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So if you ask it, you can ask something like how many project managers do we have available in Q1 26 or something that it will be able to answer or make.","index":208,"end_time":762.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":751.68,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"What''s the quality of my profile?","index":209,"end_time":765.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":763.52,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Suggest profile updates and stuff like that.","index":210,"end_time":768.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":765.88,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I can give you a few prompts that really work.","index":211,"end_time":772,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":769.04,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, that''d be great.","index":212,"end_time":773.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":772.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And when we read AI search and.","index":213,"end_time":776.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":774,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, we can have those anyways.","index":214,"end_time":777.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":776.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I see like some free styling going in here.","index":215,"end_time":779.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":777.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I assume that just is supposed to be bold text.","index":216,"end_time":781.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":779.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Then the other one.","index":217,"end_time":785.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":784.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Just watching this much.","index":218,"end_time":792.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":792.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So this starts out going through searching for a web developer, changing dates, availability, just kind of messing with all the filters.","index":219,"end_time":804.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":796.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I wouldn''t use.","index":220,"end_time":806.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":805.69,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I would.","index":221,"end_time":806.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":806.57,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I would use the other P search, the complex search that''s more impressive.","index":222,"end_time":812.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":806.93,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"This is just a free search.","index":223,"end_time":814.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":813.53,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":224,"end_time":816.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":815.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I know Hendrik, or it sounded like Hendrik, is planning on recording some.","index":225,"end_time":819.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":816.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So if you have things in mind.","index":226,"end_time":822.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":820.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I can.","index":227,"end_time":824.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":822.45,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I can talk to him.","index":228,"end_time":824.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":824.01,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I haven''t done that yet.","index":229,"end_time":825.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":824.69,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":230,"end_time":826.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":825.93,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"All right.","index":231,"end_time":829.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":828.97,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":232,"end_time":830.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":829.93,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"All right, cool.","index":233,"end_time":832.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":831.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then the other thing, Eli, since we talked on Tuesday, was.","index":234,"end_time":835.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":832.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you guys were recording the videos, but also Riverside.","index":235,"end_time":838.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":836.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It looks like you had a chance to log in.","index":236,"end_time":841.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":839.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It looks like you set up this studio right here, maybe.","index":237,"end_time":843.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":841.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":238,"end_time":845.98,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":845.5,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":239,"end_time":847.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":846.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So did you play around with anything.","index":240,"end_time":849.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":847.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Or did you just set up the studio?","index":241,"end_time":851.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":849.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I didn''t play around with too much.","index":242,"end_time":853.78,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":852.38,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"I checked it out a little.","index":243,"end_time":854.78,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":853.78,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Okay.","index":244,"end_time":855.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":855.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And David, have you had a chance to log in at all?","index":245,"end_time":857.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":855.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No.","index":246,"end_time":859.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":858.78,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"Okay, no worries.","index":247,"end_time":860.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":859.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''ll get the link that''s in the chat.","index":248,"end_time":864.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":861.74,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"Is it somewhere?","index":249,"end_time":864.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":864.26,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"Yeah, I put the login in the chat.","index":250,"end_time":866.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":864.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so what I''m going to show you.","index":251,"end_time":868.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":866.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we have like the production studio here, and every time we record a new episode, we''re going to create a new studio.","index":252,"end_time":874.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":868.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''ll call this, you know, Eli and David Test just as an example.","index":253,"end_time":881.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":874.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''ll create hit new project.","index":254,"end_time":884.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":882.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so what we can do, we can plan.","index":255,"end_time":886.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":885.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So once we start getting, if we get some Fujitsu team members or computer center, etc.","index":256,"end_time":892.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":886.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You can hit plan and then you can name the session.","index":257,"end_time":895.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":892.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, you and them, your.","index":258,"end_time":896.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":895.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Your guys names, pick the date, the time, and then send them an invite.","index":259,"end_time":901.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":896.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And what''ll happen is a calendar event will pop up on their calendar tool and it''ll have a link for them.","index":260,"end_time":908.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":901.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To join as a guest.","index":261,"end_time":909.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":908.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so David, you would essentially get that from Eli for this first recording.","index":262,"end_time":913.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":910.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":263,"end_time":914.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":914.42,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"And can you do like rehearsals or something?","index":264,"end_time":918.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":916.02,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Or how does it work?","index":265,"end_time":919.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":918.58,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I''m sorry, Rehearsals?","index":266,"end_time":921.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":920.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":267,"end_time":923.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":922.18,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"You can jump in and oftentimes, like, because we record internal shows too, I''m.","index":268,"end_time":928.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":923.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hopping on a few a month.","index":269,"end_time":929.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":928.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ll take the first couple of minutes and just have a conversation and then.","index":270,"end_time":932.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":929.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''Ll turn record on.","index":271,"end_time":933.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":932.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Or you can turn record on and.","index":272,"end_time":936.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":934.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Have a test and then hop out and hop back in and start the actual show.","index":273,"end_time":940.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":936.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And it doesn''t have to be one like flawless.","index":274,"end_time":943.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":941.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You can, you can say like, okay, let''s cut that out or count back in.","index":275,"end_time":948.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":943.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We edit the whole thing and we look for those moments as well.","index":276,"end_time":951.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":948.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we should do like a try once and see how it goes.","index":277,"end_time":957.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":953.19,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, and I offered before.","index":278,"end_time":959.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":957.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I offered to join in the first recording and I can be what''s called a producer in Riverside.","index":279,"end_time":965.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":960.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we''re out.","index":280,"end_time":966.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":965.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Not on the screen.","index":281,"end_time":966.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":966.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But I''m just helping you guys with the setup.","index":282,"end_time":968.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":966.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we.","index":283,"end_time":970.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":969.59,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"We have actually a few interviews scheduled for success Stories.","index":284,"end_time":974.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":970.11,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Actually, we had one today, but it got canceled because that guy is also on sick leave.","index":285,"end_time":978.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":974.67,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"But they were in German.","index":286,"end_time":979.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":979.02,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"And what we want to do is, we want to do.","index":287,"end_time":983.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":979.98,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"We want to write success stories from that.","index":288,"end_time":985.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":983.1,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"But could we also do that with.","index":289,"end_time":986.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":985.02,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Hey, Rich.","index":290,"end_time":986.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":986.42,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"With just doing it in teams and record teams?","index":291,"end_time":989.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":986.9,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, you could do it with teams or you could do it in Riverside.","index":292,"end_time":991.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":989.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, Riverside.","index":293,"end_time":993.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":992.06,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I mean, what''s the difference between like recording a teams meeting and Riverside?","index":294,"end_time":997.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":993.18,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Riverside is.","index":295,"end_time":997.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":997.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is it''s recording you both separately in hd.","index":296,"end_time":1000.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":997.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''re basically able to have a recording of them, a recording view, and a recording of you guys together.","index":297,"end_time":1006.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1001.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we''re able to make a bunch of different assets out of it, but it records you guys both in hd.","index":298,"end_time":1010.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1006.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that Internet connection and things that.","index":299,"end_time":1011.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1010.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Might be like a blip in teams or zoom for a second or a.","index":300,"end_time":1015.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1011.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Few seconds, you don''t see that in Riverside.","index":301,"end_time":1017.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1015.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And it''s creating a transcript.","index":302,"end_time":1022.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1020.02,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, it creates a transcript.","index":303,"end_time":1023.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1022.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It creates even like AI generated previews and cuts.","index":304,"end_time":1028.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1024.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Maybe we should use that for the success story interviews.","index":305,"end_time":1032.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1030.42,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I think that would be great.","index":306,"end_time":1033.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1032.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And that could be great.","index":307,"end_time":1034.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1034.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Social content and website content.","index":308,"end_time":1036.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1034.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, where''s the license model?","index":309,"end_time":1042.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1040.11,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Is there.","index":310,"end_time":1043.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1042.71,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"You pay by what, like monthly or how does it work?","index":311,"end_time":1046.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1043.31,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So we.","index":312,"end_time":1046.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1046.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re a partner with data.","index":313,"end_time":1048.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1046.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m sorry, with Riverside.","index":314,"end_time":1049.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1048.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we get you guys a discount on our plan.","index":315,"end_time":1051.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1049.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, it''s a.","index":316,"end_time":1052.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1051.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s at a monthly pace.","index":317,"end_time":1053.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1052.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Can we use your plan then for the industry?","index":318,"end_time":1055.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1053.71,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s.","index":319,"end_time":1055.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1055.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s what you''re on.","index":320,"end_time":1056.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1055.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":321,"end_time":1056.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1056.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And that''s the login.","index":322,"end_time":1058.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1057.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, you sent me a link.","index":323,"end_time":1059.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1058.91,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I haven''t.","index":324,"end_time":1060.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1059.87,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I haven''t logged in.","index":325,"end_time":1060.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1060.15,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, there''s a login in teams if you need me to resend it.","index":326,"end_time":1063.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1061.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you can''t find it, just let me know.","index":327,"end_time":1064.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1063.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But I sent that on Tuesday.","index":328,"end_time":1065.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1064.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":329,"end_time":1066.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1065.78,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I asked them to use that one then.","index":330,"end_time":1067.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1066.14,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":331,"end_time":1068.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1067.74,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"And essentially, so, you know, if we were hopping into record.","index":332,"end_time":1072.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1068.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I''d be.","index":333,"end_time":1077.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1077.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The host is Eli.","index":334,"end_time":1078.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1077.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I use headphones.","index":335,"end_time":1080.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1079.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Headphones are recommended.","index":336,"end_time":1081.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1080.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I can also send over a video so you guys can watch it in your own time.","index":337,"end_time":1084.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1081.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Just to reference.","index":338,"end_time":1085.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1084.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m not going to select it now.","index":339,"end_time":1087.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1086.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Because it''ll turn my mic and headphones focus on Riverside instead of in the zoom conversation.","index":340,"end_time":1091.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1087.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But.","index":341,"end_time":1091.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1091.54,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"But essentially all you do is hit join studio.","index":342,"end_time":1094.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1091.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The guest will come in.","index":343,"end_time":1095.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1094.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''ll have guest written here.","index":344,"end_time":1096.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1095.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They''ll say they just connect their webcam, microphone and headphones, or indicate if they''re.","index":345,"end_time":1101.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1096.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Not using headphones and join the studio as a guest.","index":346,"end_time":1103.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1101.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Then you just have your conversation.","index":347,"end_time":1105.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1104.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"When you''re ready to hit go, hit.","index":348,"end_time":1107.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1105.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Record, and that''s pretty much it.","index":349,"end_time":1108.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1107.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, sounds good.","index":350,"end_time":1113.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1111.53,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I forward that to Bettina, who''s setting up the meetings.","index":351,"end_time":1117.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1113.21,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":352,"end_time":1120.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1120.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so you can just go in.","index":353,"end_time":1122.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1120.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And say, you know, customer X.","index":354,"end_time":1125.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1122.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You.","index":355,"end_time":1127.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1127.67,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Know, testimonial or whatever, you can name.","index":356,"end_time":1129.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1127.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The studio anything you want.","index":357,"end_time":1130.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1129.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then you just hit plan whatever date they''re willing to meet and hop.","index":358,"end_time":1135.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1131.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"On, send this to them.","index":359,"end_time":1136.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1135.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They would get an invite link to join.","index":360,"end_time":1138.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1136.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, good.","index":361,"end_time":1141.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1140.31,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"All right, Eli, those were the two things that we had talked about covering.","index":362,"end_time":1150.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1147.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Since Tuesday, especially since the campaign is still in learning phase on paid and.","index":363,"end_time":1155.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1150.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And just getting through connections sent out and emails sent out.","index":364,"end_time":1158.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1155.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is there anything else that you guys wanted to cover?","index":365,"end_time":1160.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1158.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, those are the two things.","index":366,"end_time":1165.6,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1164.24,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"I guess we could kind of as a team.","index":367,"end_time":1168.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1166.32,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Talk about what the best next steps would be in terms of both those projects though.","index":368,"end_time":1175.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1169.61,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":369,"end_time":1176.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1176.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So as soon as it sounds like Axel is going to connect with you and Hendrick on the screen recordings and.","index":370,"end_time":1182.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1176.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What content he wants shown in there.","index":371,"end_time":1184.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1182.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"From there we would begin animating those.","index":372,"end_time":1187.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1185.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then do a voiceover tied to the script and everything like that.","index":373,"end_time":1192.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1189.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Cool.","index":374,"end_time":1195.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1194.82,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"And then once you guys record your episode, you and David.","index":375,"end_time":1197.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1195.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And like I said, if you want.","index":376,"end_time":1199.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1198.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Me there, let''s just arrange scheduling a.","index":377,"end_time":1201.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1199.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Time that works for all of us.","index":378,"end_time":1202.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1201.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I''m happy to join as a.","index":379,"end_time":1205.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1204.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Producer to help with any technical questions.","index":380,"end_time":1207.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1205.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But once that''s recorded, our turnaround time.","index":381,"end_time":1210.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1208.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is typically seven days on assets.","index":382,"end_time":1212.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1210.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Cool.","index":383,"end_time":1215.06,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1214.58,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Okay.","index":384,"end_time":1215.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1215.22,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"And so you''ll get a long form.","index":385,"end_time":1217.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1215.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So it will be posted to Spotify and Apple Podcast.","index":386,"end_time":1220.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1217.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You''ll get a long form, MP4, MP3, three or four short form videos that are about 30 to a minute and.","index":387,"end_time":1230.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1221.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"A half, 30 seconds to a minute.","index":388,"end_time":1231.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1230.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And a half, as well as some.","index":389,"end_time":1233.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1231.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Quote cards and title cards and things like that.","index":390,"end_time":1235.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1233.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, you want to do this on Monday, David?","index":391,"end_time":1240.11,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1238.27,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Does that work?","index":392,"end_time":1240.75,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1240.11,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m fine Monday, apart from.","index":393,"end_time":1244.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1241.47,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"Let me just double check.","index":394,"end_time":1248.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1246.68,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"Apart from I''ve got a 10am but I''m not sure what time works for you, Eli, so presume.","index":395,"end_time":1256.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1250.04,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"Yeah, much, much later than 10, much later.","index":396,"end_time":1258.28,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1256.04,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"So you have a script and everything.","index":397,"end_time":1261.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1259.56,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay, so I''ve looked at it, honestly.","index":398,"end_time":1263.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1261.16,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"But David, you have looked at it or.","index":399,"end_time":1265.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1263.6,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":400,"end_time":1266.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1266.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So Eli''s got.","index":401,"end_time":1267.88,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1266.72,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Got what I''ve suggested.","index":402,"end_time":1270,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1268.04,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"There''s a couple of questions in there for you, Axel, as technical points, I just need to quantify.","index":403,"end_time":1274.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1270,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"I''m saying the right thing.","index":404,"end_time":1276.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1274.99,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"Oh, where''s.","index":405,"end_time":1277.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1276.83,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Can you send me, Is there a link or something I can look at?","index":406,"end_time":1280.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1277.47,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I sent you on the email, I can ref forward it.","index":407,"end_time":1282.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1280.35,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"Yeah, I think.","index":408,"end_time":1284.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1283.71,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Oh yeah, that''s a while ago, right?","index":409,"end_time":1286.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1285.15,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I think.","index":410,"end_time":1287.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1286.83,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":411,"end_time":1288.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1287.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you can send it again.","index":412,"end_time":1289.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1288.15,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, I checked that.","index":413,"end_time":1291.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1289.71,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, I did it just before I went away.","index":414,"end_time":1293.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1291.55,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"So you got something to review.","index":415,"end_time":1295.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1293.71,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"So yeah, I''ll send that over to you in a couple of minutes.","index":416,"end_time":1298.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1295.95,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"Okay, good.","index":417,"end_time":1299.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1298.62,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"All right.","index":418,"end_time":1301.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1301.42,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yes.","index":419,"end_time":1303.62,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1303.18,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Some parts of the script are like a bit general.","index":420,"end_time":1306.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1303.62,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"I don''t know if we want to keep it like that in terms of more conversational tone or that''s probably a better way to do it.","index":421,"end_time":1315.7,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1307.26,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Right?","index":422,"end_time":1315.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1315.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":423,"end_time":1316.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1315.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I don''t like to think of it as like a script.","index":424,"end_time":1318.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1316.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t want to put words in your guys mouth.","index":425,"end_time":1320.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1318.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I was more trying to provide a framework of like hey, you know, doing some research.","index":426,"end_time":1323.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1320.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This is what I think people will be interested in hearing.","index":427,"end_time":1325.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1324.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"David has a lot of things to touch on from his career journey, both as before working with data assessment or Dusty Dolo from the customer side, the challenges he was facing, why he chose you as a solution and then ultimately.","index":428,"end_time":1339.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1326.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Him joining the team.","index":429,"end_time":1340.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1339.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":430,"end_time":1344.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1343.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I put a few things that I thought were probably relevant to talk about Colin on a, on a couple of A4 pages just to keep some track of some, some thought process if you like to give me a nudge for me to answer.","index":431,"end_time":1359.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1344.03,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"So that''s what I''ve just put on a little bit of paper and I''d looked into a couple of things that were happening out in the marketplace as well that might be relevant, especially around the AI bit which is where Axel just needs to confirm that he''s okay that we touch on them.","index":432,"end_time":1375.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1359.45,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"Yeah, I have, I''m not in, I have an all day workshop on Monday, so I''m not in on Monday and I''m, I have another workshop on Tuesday.","index":433,"end_time":1384.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1376.18,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So probably.","index":434,"end_time":1385.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1384.74,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, I can probably not do anything before Wednesday.","index":435,"end_time":1389.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1387.78,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So.","index":436,"end_time":1390.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1390.58,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":437,"end_time":1392.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1390.98,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"So should we catch up on Wednesday, Eli.","index":438,"end_time":1394.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1392.1,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"Have a view first and then, then we can, we can go through the details.","index":439,"end_time":1401.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1396.34,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"All right.","index":440,"end_time":1402.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1401.79,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":441,"end_time":1402.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1402.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And just Wednesday''s perfect.","index":442,"end_time":1404.43,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1402.87,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Some tips.","index":443,"end_time":1405.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1404.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s not like a live news broadcast, you know, make.","index":444,"end_time":1409.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1405.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You can make mistakes, don''t worry about it.","index":445,"end_time":1411.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1409.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You can count yourself back in.","index":446,"end_time":1412.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1411.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":447,"end_time":1412.95,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1412.31,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"You can say scratch that out when you send it over.","index":448,"end_time":1415.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1412.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You can say like hey, you know, I get some things like hey, my dog walked into the frame around 20 minutes in.","index":449,"end_time":1422.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1415.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like can we just edit that part out?","index":450,"end_time":1424.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1422.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Because we counted back in you know, anything that you guys are worried about.","index":451,"end_time":1427.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1424.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like that, just send it over.","index":452,"end_time":1429.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1427.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We do course through the episode looking for those.","index":453,"end_time":1431.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1429.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We also clean up the ums and ahs and things like that.","index":454,"end_time":1434.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1431.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we''ll put.","index":455,"end_time":1436.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1435.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ll have the transcript, episode titles, show.","index":456,"end_time":1440.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1437.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Notes, and everything like that all built out as well.","index":457,"end_time":1442.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1440.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you should have very little ums and arms, but you might have a few sos from me, Colin.","index":458,"end_time":1448.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1443.43,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"That''s usually my go.","index":459,"end_time":1449.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1448.51,"speaker_name":"osbal"},{"text":"And it''s up to you if you want us to leave those in there.","index":460,"end_time":1451.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1449.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Everyone''s got a different preference on the.","index":461,"end_time":1454.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1451.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Output of the video.","index":462,"end_time":1455.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1454.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So through this first project and maybe even the second, we''ll just learn your personal preferences of what you want included.","index":463,"end_time":1460.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1455.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And what you don''t.","index":464,"end_time":1461.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1460.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we''ll, you know, we typically.","index":465,"end_time":1464.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1461.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Get to like, first round of assets being approved.","index":466,"end_time":1466.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1464.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And if at any point we want to change the assets that are produced.","index":467,"end_time":1472.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1469.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you guys want more short form videos and less quote cards, more of both, a whole different asset, we can.","index":468,"end_time":1477.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1472.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Talk about that as well.","index":469,"end_time":1478.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1477.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":470,"end_time":1482.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1480.62,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"All right.","index":471,"end_time":1483.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1483.25,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":472,"end_time":1484.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1484.29,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Excited to get a few of those episodes because then we can make that podcast landing page.","index":473,"end_time":1489.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1485.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then also if we get the customer testimonials, that''d be great to build a page on as well and include.","index":474,"end_time":1495.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1489.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sprinkled throughout the other pages that we''ve created.","index":475,"end_time":1497.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1495.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":476,"end_time":1500.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1499.01,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"All right.","index":477,"end_time":1501.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1501.33,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, thank you all.","index":478,"end_time":1503.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1502.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Have a great weekend.","index":479,"end_time":1504.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1503.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You too.","index":480,"end_time":1505.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1504.69,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":481,"end_time":1505.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1505.21,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay, bye.","index":482,"end_time":1506.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1505.73,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"}],"dateString":"2025-12-05T14:00:00.000Z","host_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86344108572?pwd=qdakcUFJbrjywReJlBZ3DxNLrBYqXb.1","participants":["tristan.pelligrino@marketersindemand.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,joachim.giesen@uni-jena.de,guille.santana@marketersindemand.com,voelker@data-assessment.com,bebinger@decidalo.com,osbaldeston@data-assessment.com,pollex@data-assessment.com","tristan.pelligrino@marketersindemand.com","joachim.giesen@uni-jena.de","guille.santana@marketersindemand.com","voelker@data-assessment.com","bebinger@decidalo.com","osbaldeston@data-assessment.com","pollex@data-assessment.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KB5M0D59RQRV673GHF7ERSH5","organizer_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.87,"bullets":["Discussed new LinkedIn outreach sequence; 36 connections sent, 3 accepted, 2 messages delivered.","Reviewed AI tool''s functionality; Axel to provide effective prompts for targeted responses.","Agreed to record success stories using Riverside for higher quality and editing flexibility.","Outlined asset delivery plan: 7-day turnaround for long/short videos, transcripts, and quote cards.","Scheduled follow-up coordination on script inputs and recording preferences for Wednesday."],"highlights":[{"quote":"You''ll get a long form, MP4, MP3, three or four short form videos...","speaker":"Colin Costigan"},{"quote":"Maybe we should use that for the success story interviews.","speaker":"Axel Völker"},{"quote":"Some parts of the script are like a bit general... more conversational tone.","speaker":"Eli Bebinger"}],"topics":["delivery","AI","recording","engagement","assets"],"model":"openai/gpt-4","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-12-05T19:33:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Campaign Performance and Lead Engagement**\n\nThe team is still in the early phase of the new outreach campaign, with initial connection and messaging activity underway but limited replies received so far (09:11).\n\n- **Since Tuesday, 36 new connections** have been sent through the new sequence, with **3 accepted and 2 messages sent** from Eli''s profile (09:11).\n    - Earlier replies are still coming from the old sequence, with no responses yet from the new sequence.\n    - Eli noted some feedback from one lead about unclear responses, prompting follow-up to clarify messaging.\n    - The new email sequence launched Tuesday morning, reflecting a strategic refresh to improve engagement.\n    - Monitoring this early activity helps determine if the new approach drives faster, clearer responses and better lead quality.\n\n- Colin explained that system notifications for LinkedIn replies are sent automatically when a reply hits Eli’s profile linked to the campaign (06:07).\n    - The team has access to the Hayreach platform for managing leads and can track conversation threads.\n    - Coordination around message content and sequence personalization remains important to avoid repetitive back-and-forth exchanges.\n    - Eli and Axel plan to review and possibly refine the new sequence messaging for clarity and effectiveness.\n\n## **Content Production and Media Strategy**\n\nThe team is preparing to produce and distribute recorded episodes and success stories to boost marketing and customer engagement (14:12).\n\n- **Riverside has been set up as the primary recording platform** for producing high-quality HD video and audio episodes with transcripts and AI-generated previews (16:32).\n    - Riverside records separate feeds for each participant, ensuring clean production unaffected by internet blips.\n    - The system supports planning sessions, sending calendar invites, and hosting rehearsals or test runs before recording.\n    - Colin offered to act as a producer for the first recording to assist with technical setup and smooth execution.\n    - Axel agreed to forward Riverside access and recording instructions to the team member managing meetings.\n\n- Success story interviews are scheduled but impacted by sick leave; these will be recorded via Riverside or Teams, with Riverside preferred for higher quality (16:09).\n    - The goal is to create rich social and website content from these interviews, including short-form videos, quote cards, and long-form podcasts.\n    - Colin outlined that typical post-production turnaround is about **7 days**, delivering multiple asset formats for broad use (20:15).\n    - The team will build a dedicated podcast landing page and integrate testimonials throughout the website to enhance brand storytelling.\n\n## **Script Development and Messaging Tone**\n\nThe team is refining narrative frameworks for recorded episodes to balance structure with natural conversation (21:43).\n\n- David prepared a detailed 2-page outline covering relevant topics and marketplace trends, especially around AI-related content, for review by Axel (22:24).\n    - Axel needs to confirm technical accuracy before finalizing content to align messaging with product capabilities.\n    - Eli prefers a conversational tone over a strict script to allow natural flow and authenticity in recordings.\n    - Colin emphasized flexible frameworks rather than rigid scripts, aiming to highlight David’s career journey and customer perspective naturally.\n\n- Scheduling constraints mean Axel will join detailed review sessions starting Wednesday after workshops, delaying some approvals (22:56).\n    - The team agreed to meet Wednesday to finalize script details and technical input before recording.\n    - Colin encouraged the team to be relaxed during recordings, noting post-production can edit out mistakes, ums, and interruptions.\n\n## **AI Features and Internal Tools Progress**\n\nThe AI-powered profile assistance and search features are in early beta but showing promising capabilities to enhance user experience (10:32).\n\n- Eli and Hendrick have been creating screen recordings to showcase AI functionalities, focusing on profile help and complex people search (12:27).\n    - Axel noted the current AI mostly links to documentation but can answer specific queries about resource availability and profile quality.\n    - The team plans to customize AI prompts and responses to improve relevance and usability based on feedback.\n    - The complex search tool was recommended over the basic free search for better demonstration and user value.\n\n- Colin and Axel discussed further developing AI capabilities to support profile improvements and resource planning insights.\n    - This aligns with longer-term plans to integrate AI as a value differentiator in product offerings.\n    - The team will continue refining AI features while managing expectations around current beta limitations.\n\n## **Operational Coordination and Next Steps**\n\nClear ownership and timelines were established to advance both content production and campaign activities efficiently (19:36).\n\n- Axel will connect with Eli and Hendrick to finalize screen recording content and priorities for animation and voiceover production (19:36).\n    - Once recorded, the production turnaround is about **7 days** to deliver polished assets.\n    - Colin offered to schedule and produce the first recording session with Eli and David on Monday, pending availability.\n    - David confirmed Monday availability except for a 10 AM commitment; Eli preferred a later time.\n\n- A follow-up meeting is planned for Wednesday to review scripts and technical points with Axel after his workshops (22:56).\n    - This ensures all messaging aligns with product capabilities and marketplace positioning.\n    - The team will use this session to finalize next steps on both the media content and campaign messaging fronts.\n\n- Colin emphasized flexible asset production, adapting formats and quantities (short videos, quote cards) based on team preferences and audience response over time.\n    - This iterative approach aims to maximize content impact and efficiency.\n    - The end goal is a cohesive marketing ecosystem with podcasts, testimonials, and lead nurturing integrated smoothly.","outline":null,"keywords":["LinkedIn Campaign","Riverside Recording","AI Profile Assistant","Video Production","Marketing Assets","Podcast Recording"],"overview":"- **New Campaign Status:** 36 new connections sent; 3 accepted so far, with follow-ups needed for clearer messaging.\n\n- **Content Production Setup:** Riverside established for recording; aiming for high-quality episodes and quick turnaround of about 7 days.\n\n- **Script Development Focus:** Balance structure and natural tone in recordings; detailed outlines and flexible frameworks encouraged for authenticity.\n\n- **AI Tool Progress:** AI features in beta show promise; plans to enhance capabilities for better user experience and resource insights.\n\n- **Operational Coordination:** Clear timelines set; follow-up meeting scheduled to review scripts and finalize production details for content.\n\n- **Flexible Asset Production:** Adapt format based on feedback; goal is integrated marketing ecosystem with podcasts, testimonials, and lead nurturing.","action_items":"\n**Colin Costigan**\nResend Hayreach system login credentials to the team to enable access and review of new campaign replies (07:34)\nSchedule and facilitate initial podcast recording session with Eli and David, acting as producer to help with technical support (15:40)\nProduce marketing assets from recordings including long form podcasts, short videos, quote cards, and transcripts within 7 days turnaround after recording (19:54)\n\n**Eli Bebinger**\nFollow up on LinkedIn responses and manage messaging sequences, ensure new campaign messages are being sent out (07:16)\nShare screen recordings and AI interaction videos in SharePoint/chat and collaborate with Axel and Hendrick on content for animations (10:58)\n\n**Axel Völker**\nReview and provide feedback on script and technical points shared by David Osbaldeston prior to recordings (21:10)\nCoordinate with Hendrick on recording and screening videos and provide prompts for AI capabilities demonstrations (12:52)\n\n**David Osbaldeston**\nForward updated script and technical details to Axel for review (21:27)\n\n**Eli Bebinger & David Osbaldeston**\nPrepare and conduct recording session on Monday, keeping it conversational and flexible for edits (20:38)\n\n**Axel Völker & Eli Bebinger**\nPlan follow-up meeting on Wednesday to review recordings and script adjustments post-Axel’s workshop (23:10)\n\n**Bettina (via Axel)**\nManage scheduling of customer success stories interviews using Riverside platform (18:09)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"eabdb785-7d4a-4200-83c0-e7fe1b8443b9","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
