  '[{"text":"Resend Hayreach system login credentials to the team to enable access and review of new campaign replies (07:34)","completed":false},{"text":"Schedule and facilitate initial podcast recording session with Eli and David, acting as producer to help with technical support (15:40)","completed":false},{"text":"Produce marketing assets from recordings including long form podcasts, short videos, quote cards, and transcripts within 7 days turnaround after recording (19:54)","completed":false},{"text":"Follow up on LinkedIn responses and manage messaging sequences, ensure new campaign messages are being sent out (07:16)","completed":false},{"text":"Share screen recordings and AI interaction videos in SharePoint/chat and collaborate with Axel and Hendrick on content for animations (10:58)","completed":false},{"text":"Review and provide feedback on script and technical points shared by David Osbaldeston prior to recordings (21:10)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate with Hendrick on recording and screening videos and provide prompts for AI capabilities demonstrations (12:52)","completed":false},{"text":"Forward updated script and technical details to Axel for review (21:27)","completed":false},{"text":"Prepare and conduct recording session on Monday, keeping it conversational and flexible for edits (20:38)","completed":false},{"text":"Plan follow-up meeting on Wednesday to review recordings and script adjustments post-Axel’s workshop (23:10)","completed":false},{"text":"Manage scheduling of customer success stories interviews using Riverside platform (18:09)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
