":"Yeah, some you can''t see in Google Preview.","index":183,"end_time":652.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":648.54,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"No, I did the markup thing.","index":184,"end_time":656.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":653.99,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, let me pull those up.","index":185,"end_time":659.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":656.31,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"It.","index":186,"end_time":679.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":679.36,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"So is that going to the same target group?","index":187,"end_time":716.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":714.49,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I think you said you wanted to.","index":188,"end_time":717.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":716.13,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"To refine the target group.","index":189,"end_time":719.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":717.61,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Also.","index":190,"end_time":719.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":719.17,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"We have still a lot of names that we haven''t touched yet in that same cohort.","index":191,"end_time":730.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":724.73,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Is there for the ads.","index":192,"end_time":735.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":733.6,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I thought the ads somehow some LinkedIn magic.","index":193,"end_time":738.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":735.04,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"How they.","index":194,"end_time":738.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":738.48,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Oh, for that piece.","index":195,"end_time":740.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":739.52,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean it would just be based on the custom audience that we have with the new folks that we''ll put in the group.","index":196,"end_time":747.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":740.96,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"So yeah, we always have to adjust the custom audience based on the names that we drop in email and LinkedIn.","index":197,"end_time":757.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":748.48,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Yeah, the first.","index":198,"end_time":760.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":759.97,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Do you see my comments there?","index":199,"end_time":762.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":761.25,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, the first comment is if you.","index":200,"end_time":763.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":762.41,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I mean, I''m a bit concerned that the audience and LinkedIn is again like very generic.","index":201,"end_time":771.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":763.93,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"And if you put AI and resource management, then they may think this is like a computational resources or something like cloud AI computing stuff.","index":202,"end_time":783.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":771.97,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Because Azure and aws, they also have things called resource managers that manage your.","index":203,"end_time":790.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":784.88,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I don''t know, whatever your GPUs or something.","index":204,"end_time":793.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":791.92,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"And so I thought maybe let''s call it workforce management to make clear that we''re not talking about technical computing resources here.","index":205,"end_time":803.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":794.24,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":206,"end_time":804.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":803.68,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Because I think from it looks like that people only read the header because we noticed that people clicked.","index":207,"end_time":812.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":804.24,"speaker_name":"Axel Völk