xel Völker"},{"text":"And then just message three it is.","index":336,"end_time":1249.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1247.22,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, so, yeah, I see what you''re saying there.","index":337,"end_time":1255.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1250.98,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Yeah, we can, we can adjust that phrasing at the end.","index":338,"end_time":1259.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1257.06,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"We could say we, we actually have, we''ll change the phrasing to, you know, we actually have a free version of the product if you''d like to test out, you know.","index":339,"end_time":1269.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1259.54,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Yeah, we put that in message one or two or whatever.","index":340,"end_time":1272.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1269.46,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":341,"end_time":1273.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1272.46,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, these.","index":342,"end_time":1275.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1275.02,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Yeah, we can look at that.","index":343,"end_time":1278.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1276.94,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Yeah, I see what you''re saying, though, now.","index":344,"end_time":1281.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1279.42,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Okay, I thought that was the email there.","index":345,"end_time":1282.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1281.1,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"All right, perfect.","index":346,"end_time":1283.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1282.74,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Okay, so you adjust that then.","index":347,"end_time":1286.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1284.7,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"All right, so, yep, those, those adjustments there we''ll make.","index":348,"end_time":129