uences, but.","index":360,"end_time":1340.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1337.57,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"But yeah, the email in.","index":361,"end_time":1344.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1340.53,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"In LinkedIn we doesn''t drip as fast anyway because we''re able to.","index":362,"end_time":1348.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1344.17,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"To send more emails out at a, at a faster clip just because of the volume in the domains.","index":363,"end_time":1353.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1348.17,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"So we can launch LinkedIn and I think that we could do Wednesday or Thursday, that would be fine.","index":364,"end_time":1360.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1353.73,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Or maybe, maybe GA Friday.","index":365,"end_time":1364.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1361.38,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"That way we''re not hitting people up on a holiday because we won''t.","index":366,"end_time":1368.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1364.9,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Can you share?","index":367,"end_time":1370.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1369.46,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"What?","index":368,"end_time":1370.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1370.1,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Can you let me know once you made the updates and shared it again?","index":369,"end_time":1373.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1370.499,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Sort of.","index":370,"end_time":1374.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1373.46,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":371,"end_time":1374.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1374.1,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Now that GA''s got teams, we''ll make sure we get all the final links out to you.","index":372,"end_time":1382.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1375.7,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"I know she''s working on getting those in place today, so.","index":373,"end_time":1385.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1382.04,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Yeah, so I think what we could do is launch LinkedIn on Friday and then get the smart lead campaigns on Monday and then same thing with the.","index":374,"end_time":1394.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1386.76,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"The ads we''ll push.","index":375,"end_time":1395.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1394.64,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"We''ll make sure those are adjusted and then those get rolled out as well.","index":376,"end_time":1399.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1395.68,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Okay.","index":377,"end_time":1403.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1403.32,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":378,"end_time":1404.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1404.44,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"All right.","index":379,"end_time":1406.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1406.21,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"So moving.","index":380,"end_time":1408.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1406.93,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"I wanna.","index":381,"end_time":1409.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1408.85,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"You wanna.","index":382,"end_time":1410.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1409.53,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So you are not in, I guess then more or less the rest of the week or.","index":383,"end_time":1413.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1410.05,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, tomorrow you are.","index":384,"end_time":1415.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1414.45,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m in and out tomorrow.","index":385,"end_time":1418.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1416.53,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"I''ll be syncing up with GA as we get this stuff in place a