-- Meeting: Powerhouse Gym & Ideometry: Weekly Sync (2025-12-03 16:00:00+00)
WITH new_meeting AS (
  INSERT INTO compass_meetings (contract_id, meeting_date, source, external_id, title, participants, duration_seconds, recording_url, transcript, sentiment, raw_metadata, created_at, updated_at)
  VALUES (
    'e7336694-2c40-4fcf-a7ef-4d0460f053c8',
    '2025-12-03 16:00:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01KB35HD2DB1VKXJ12JTM0CRX6',
    'Powerhouse Gym & Ideometry: Weekly Sync',
    '{"Colin Costigan","Nina Belina","Robert","Milan Wagner"}'::text[],
    1286,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86061042503?pwd=x0TBEgRs7qFmrRIEItauCzbH71kaq8.1',
    '{"id":"01KB35HD2DB1VKXJ12JTM0CRX6","title":"Powerhouse Gym & Ideometry: Weekly Sync","summary":{"notes":"## **Sales Performance and Lead Management**\n\nThe team is seeing positive momentum with a strong sales month in November, signaling a promising holiday season.\n\n- **November marked the best sales month of the year**, indicating customers are starting holiday shopping early, according to Robert (06:25)  \n    - This uptick suggests the sales pipeline is active and ready for end-of-year campaigns  \n    - Robert’s optimism sets a positive baseline for forecasting December performance  \n    - Maintaining this momentum requires close monitoring of lead flow and conversion rates  \n    - This context justifies ramping up outreach efforts and marketing support for the holiday period\n\n- **Lead management system issues with HubSpot and Air Call were resolved**, ensuring sales contacts and calls sync properly, Milan confirmed (08:31)  \n    - Earlier problems caused duplicate or incomplete contact records, impacting follow-up accuracy  \n    - Fixing this restores sales team efficiency and data quality for pipeline tracking  \n    - Milan emphasized team adjustment to new systems is ongoing, highlighting training needs  \n    - Resolving these sync issues reduces risk of lost leads and missed sales opportunities\n\n## **Website Content and Messaging Updates**\n\nImmediate website content fixes are planned to better reflect the brand’s positioning and improve customer engagement.\n\n- **A video on the website needs replacing with an updated tour video from the content team**, Milan committed to deliver it soon (10:03)  \n    - Colin and Nina confirmed they have access to Squarespace but await the new video file  \n    - Updating the video will better showcase the facility and enhance visitor conversion  \n    - This content refresh supports the upcoming New Year’s resolution marketing push  \n    - Timely video replacement is vital to keep the site fresh and competitive\n\n- **The phrase “luxury at a lower price” on the site will be removed or reworded** to align with brand integrity, Milan noted (14:12)  \n    - Milan suggested luxury messaging should not imply discounting, to maintain premium appeal  \n    - Colin committed to searching the site and making necessary edits quickly  \n    - Clear, consistent messaging is key to differentiating from competitors  \n    - Adjusting this language supports the brand’s long-term positioning strategy\n\n## **SMS Marketing Strategy and Cost Management**\n\nThe team is planning a targeted SMS campaign to boost engagement, balancing message volume with budget constraints.\n\n- **Estimated SMS volume could reach about 25,000 messages per month**, covering new leads, existing pipeline, and past due reminders, Milan explained (16:11)  \n    - Colin noted this number is on the high end but plausible given lead flow and member base  \n    - HubSpot’s SMS pricing approximates under **$1,000 per month**, depending on volume (17:18)  \n    - Milan will reconnect with the SMS vendor rep to explore trial options or discounts (19:56)  \n    - Testing limited segments first will help measure ROI before full rollout\n\n- **ROI measurement will focus on response rates and membership activation or payment completion**, Colin outlined (18:08)  \n    - Text responses converting to active memberships or payments will demonstrate campaign success  \n    - Prioritizing past due payment reminders via SMS may yield immediate revenue impact  \n    - This approach reduces wasted spend and informs future scaling decisions  \n    - Milan plans to analyze message effectiveness with the team before final commitments\n\n## **Contract Status and Service Availability**\n\nThe team confirmed ongoing support and service availability through mid-year, ensuring continuity for upcoming initiatives.\n\n- **Existing service contract with Colin’s team is active through June**, Colin confirmed (20:24)  \n    - This provides a runway for additional HubSpot work, including email campaigns and sequences  \n    - The team can deploy creative support such as social media posts aligned with seasonal promotions  \n    - This flexibility allows for adaptive marketing tactics based on sales trends and customer feedback  \n    - Robert and Milan will discuss internal priorities and return with requests to Colin’s team\n\n- **Past due HubSpot invoice from November 29 was identified and acknowledged**, Milan committed to addressing it promptly (11:23)  \n    - Timely payment will prevent service disruptions during critical marketing periods  \n    - This highlights the need for routine billing oversight to avoid operational hiccups  \n    - Colin flagged this proactively to maintain smooth platform access  \n    - Resolving it ensures uninterrupted use of essential CRM and marketing tools","outline":null,"keywords":["HubSpot","Air Call","SMS marketing","website updates","lead management","holiday sales"],"overview":"- **Strong Sales Forecast:** November had best sales month of the year, indicating strong holiday shopping momentum.  \n- **Lead Management Fixes:** HubSpot and Air Call issues resolved, improving contact syncing and sales team efficiency.  \n- **Website Content Updates:** New tour video needed for website; current content must better reflect brand integrity.  \n- **SMS Campaign Plans:** Targeted SMS campaign may send 25,000 messages monthly, costing under $1,000; ROI focused on membership activation.  \n- **Contract and Service Continuity:** Service contract active through June; creative marketing support available for ongoing campaigns.  \n- **Invoice Acknowledgement:** Past due HubSpot invoice needs prompt action to prevent service disruption during busy marketing periods.","action_items":"\n**Milan Wagner**\nNotify team that routing call info without data input must be manual due to sync limitations (09:52)\nObtain updated tour video from content team and send for website update (10:45)\nAddress past due HubSpot invoice from November 29 (11:30)\nLocate and revise/remove ''luxury at a lower price'' phrase on website (14:13)\nReach out to SMS marketing rep to request trial or negotiate terms (19:56)\nDiscuss SMS marketing strategy and message volume with Robert before follow-up with marketers (21:07)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nSwap out website video promptly once received from Milan (11:05)\nAssist with SMS marketing rep engagement or join call for negotiation if needed (17:30)\nSupport email campaigns, new sequences, social media posts, and website enhancements as needed within contract hours through June (20:21)\n\n**Robert Rudder**\nCoordinate offline discussion with Milan regarding SMS marketing volume and strategy (21:07)\n"},"duration":21.440000534057617,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Colin Costigan"},{"id":1,"name":"Nina Belina"},{"id":2,"name":"Robert"},{"id":3,"name":"Milan Wagner"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Sa.","index":0,"end_time":51.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":51.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Long time no see.","index":1,"end_time":210.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":209.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":2,"end_time":211.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":211.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":3,"end_time":215.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":214.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I saw your dog in the background on the last meeting.","index":4,"end_time":219.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":215.44,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":5,"end_time":220.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":219.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Good morning.","index":6,"end_time":235.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":235.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hey, how''s it going?","index":7,"end_time":237.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":236.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Robert.","index":8,"end_time":238.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":237.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Robert, do you know if Milan is planning on joining?","index":9,"end_time":315.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":314.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, he should be.","index":10,"end_time":317.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":316.68,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"I think he was wrapping up a previous call.","index":11,"end_time":319.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":318.2,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":12,"end_time":321.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":320.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"How are things going over there, Robert?","index":13,"end_time":381.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":380.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You''re writing a lot of New Year''s resolution plans.","index":14,"end_time":384.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":381.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We haven''t.","index":15,"end_time":386.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":385.93,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"I don''t think we''ve seen.","index":16,"end_time":387.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":386.65,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"Well, I''ll.","index":17,"end_time":389.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":388.01,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"Let me back up.","index":18,"end_time":390.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":389.69,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"We had a really good month in November, so our best.","index":19,"end_time":393.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":390.49,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"Our best month of the year, actually.","index":20,"end_time":394.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":393.45,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"So we''re starting to see, I think, some people coming in and trying to get a head start on the holidays, so hopefully that continues on.","index":21,"end_time":404.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":395.85,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"So, so far so good.","index":22,"end_time":406.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":404.73,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"It''s awesome.","index":23,"end_time":407.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":406.49,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Let me.","index":24,"end_time":415.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":414.85,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Let me shoot Milan a note and.","index":25,"end_time":417.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":415.57,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"See if he''s jumping on.","index":26,"end_time":418.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":417.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It.","index":27,"end_time":435.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":434.86,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"Hey, guys, he said he''d be on.","index":28,"end_time":481.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":479.43,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"In just a second.","index":29,"end_time":482.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":481.79,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"How we doing, guys?","index":30,"end_time":484.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":483.51,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Sorry, guys.","index":31,"end_time":488.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":487.75,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"I was doing a little coaching.","index":32,"end_time":490.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":488.19,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Ignore what I requested yesterday.","index":33,"end_time":496.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":494.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Nina.","index":34,"end_time":497.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":497.35,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yife ended up answering the question.","index":35,"end_time":500.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":498.47,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That was for Alex.","index":36,"end_time":501.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":500.23,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That''s all the.","index":37,"end_time":503.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":502.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That was all the contacts that I received, so we''re good there.","index":38,"end_time":509.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":504.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Cool.","index":39,"end_time":510.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":510.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then also with the Air Call stuff, um, from what I was understanding was there were sales being done on Data Track, and then the contacts not being created on HubSpot, and then when they were reaching out to those contacts on Air Call, then these prospect accounts with just the Number and the airCall name were being created.","index":40,"end_time":543.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":511.67,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s all been resolved, so.","index":41,"end_time":546.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":544.03,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":42,"end_time":547.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":547.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Apologies for the confusion there as well.","index":43,"end_time":550.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":548.83,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Takes time for a team to get used to new systems.","index":44,"end_time":554.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":552.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":45,"end_time":555.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":554.91,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":46,"end_time":556.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":555.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"One thing I did want to find out if we could do is if somebody calls on Air Call, and.","index":47,"end_time":565.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":557.79,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Let''S.","index":48,"end_time":568.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":568.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Say they don''t put any of the information in, are we able to route, like, the.","index":49,"end_time":574.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":568.55,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"At least the club name and the lead source and that kind of stuff?","index":50,"end_time":579.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":575.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, at the moment, no, because between error call and data check, it''s not how the sync works, so.","index":51,"end_time":589.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":581.63,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":52,"end_time":590.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":589.95,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"Okay.","index":53,"end_time":592.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":592.35,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So it''s all going to have to be.","index":54,"end_time":596.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":595.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s all manual stuff then.","index":55,"end_time":597.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":596.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":56,"end_time":599.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":598.73,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":57,"end_time":600.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":599.77,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All right, that''s fine.","index":58,"end_time":601.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":600.57,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Cool.","index":59,"end_time":603.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":602.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''ll let the team know.","index":60,"end_time":604.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":603.37,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then in terms of the website, that video that I sent over, we just need to replace that video because the tour looks like.","index":61,"end_time":617.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":605.85,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And do you guys have access to videos yet or.","index":62,"end_time":623.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":620.73,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Not yet?","index":63,"end_time":624.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":623.85,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No.","index":64,"end_time":633.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":632.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Nina, do you know if we have access to the video to swap it out?","index":65,"end_time":636.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":633.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, we have access to Squarespace, but I don''t know with which video.","index":66,"end_time":642.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":638.32,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Which would we swap it?","index":67,"end_time":644.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":642.96,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, I think you said you were getting.","index":68,"end_time":647.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":645.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, you said we need to update this, but I don''t think you ever sent the video.","index":69,"end_time":650.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":648,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I thought you guys had, like, a tour video, which is.","index":70,"end_time":656.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":652.85,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''ll get that.","index":71,"end_time":657.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":656.85,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''ll get it from our content team, and then I''ll send that over.","index":72,"end_time":664.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":661.09,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, let me get that swapped out pretty quick.","index":73,"end_time":666.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":665.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Cool, cool.","index":74,"end_time":668.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":667.41,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"There was another thing that Tara had mentioned, trying to find it here.","index":75,"end_time":677.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":669.41,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You guys have any updates for.","index":76,"end_time":679.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":677.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"For us while I look for this stuff?","index":77,"end_time":682.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":679.58,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Just one thing I noticed going into the account.","index":78,"end_time":685.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":683.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It looks like your invoice is past due for HubSpot.","index":79,"end_time":688.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":685.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, great.","index":80,"end_time":690.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":690.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":81,"end_time":692.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":691.58,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''ll reach out to you.","index":82,"end_time":694.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":693.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":83,"end_time":695.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":695.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, it looks like it was November 29th.","index":84,"end_time":699.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":697.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So Thanksgiving time.","index":85,"end_time":701.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":699.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"How was Thanksgiving?","index":86,"end_time":703.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":702.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I apologize.","index":87,"end_time":704.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":703.99,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I should have asked about the holidays.","index":88,"end_time":706.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":704.75,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It was good.","index":89,"end_time":707.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":706.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"How about you?","index":90,"end_time":707.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":707.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It was pretty good.","index":91,"end_time":709.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":708.47,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It was pretty good.","index":92,"end_time":709.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":709.27,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Spent some nice time with the family.","index":93,"end_time":711.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":710.23,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We had, like, Spanish, so we had, like, a Spanish twist to it.","index":94,"end_time":717.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":712.15,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I made the turkey, and then we had paella and, like, tortilla espanola and all that kind of stuff.","index":95,"end_time":722.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":717.27,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So it was an interesting Thanksgiving this year.","index":96,"end_time":726.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":722.27,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":97,"end_time":727.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":726.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I have a very white Thanksgiving.","index":98,"end_time":728.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":727.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Nice ham stuffing, three different types of potatoes.","index":99,"end_time":734.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":729.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":100,"end_time":736.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":735.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We did not have cornbread.","index":101,"end_time":740.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":738.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No.","index":102,"end_time":740.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":740.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh, you did?","index":103,"end_time":743,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":742.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I like cornbread.","index":104,"end_time":744.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":743,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m not usually big on sweets.","index":105,"end_time":745.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":744.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I get, like.","index":106,"end_time":746.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":745.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I have a thing with sugar.","index":107,"end_time":747.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":746.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I get, like, migraines.","index":108,"end_time":748.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":747.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":109,"end_time":749.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":749.12,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, I love cornbread.","index":110,"end_time":753.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":751.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh, my God.","index":111,"end_time":754,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":753.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Apple pie.","index":112,"end_time":755.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":754.82,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All that kind of good stuff.","index":113,"end_time":756.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":755.38,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I might be dating myself, but I don''t know if you''ve ever seen the movie.","index":114,"end_time":758.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":756.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m going get you, sucker.","index":115,"end_time":760.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":758.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, Robert, you know what I''m talking about.","index":116,"end_time":763.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":760.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s an old one.","index":117,"end_time":764.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":763.38,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":118,"end_time":764.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":764.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":119,"end_time":764.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":764.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Y'' all gonna eat y'' all cornbread?","index":120,"end_time":766.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":765.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":121,"end_time":770.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":770.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We took my daughter on a plane for the first time.","index":122,"end_time":772.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":770.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think Nina''s heard this story, like, four times this week already, but.","index":123,"end_time":775.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":772.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And of course, she got sick, so.","index":124,"end_time":778.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":776.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"10 months old, her first plane ride, and then we got sick afterwards, so.","index":125,"end_time":783.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":779.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Nice.","index":126,"end_time":784.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":784.38,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Only the good stuff.","index":127,"end_time":787.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":786.46,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":128,"end_time":788.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":787.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But I was down in Florida.","index":129,"end_time":789.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":788.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You were?","index":130,"end_time":790.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":790.06,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":131,"end_time":791.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":790.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Should have come down and said hi.","index":132,"end_time":793.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":792.06,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I don''t think I was close to.","index":133,"end_time":795.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":794.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Where were you?","index":134,"end_time":797.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":797.02,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I was in south of Naples.","index":135,"end_time":799.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":797.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":136,"end_time":800.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":800.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":137,"end_time":801.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":801.34,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Florida''s a lot bigger than I, like, ever really think until I land there.","index":138,"end_time":805.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":802.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s boring to drive Florida, too.","index":139,"end_time":809.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":806.14,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"There''s nothing to see.","index":140,"end_time":810.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":809.63,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, we went there for my honeymoon, and we would even drive from.","index":141,"end_time":814.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":810.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Because they''re, like, right near Marco Island.","index":142,"end_time":816.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":814.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we would drive from there to, like, into the city of Naples, and it''s like, there''s Just once you get there, it''s cool, but like otherwise it''s just, it''s just a road, it''s just a bunch of highways.","index":143,"end_time":825.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":816.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Couple alligators.","index":144,"end_time":827.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":826.19,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":145,"end_time":828.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":827.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Seeing those on the golf courses.","index":146,"end_time":830.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":828.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh yeah.","index":147,"end_time":831.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":830.75,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh yeah.","index":148,"end_time":832.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":831.35,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh, you''re a golfer too, man?","index":149,"end_time":833.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":832.03,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I am.","index":150,"end_time":834.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":833.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Next time let me know.","index":151,"end_time":835.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":834.67,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":152,"end_time":836.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":836.3,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Played a Tiburon a few years ago with my father in law.","index":153,"end_time":839.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":836.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":154,"end_time":841.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":839.9,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Shot a 38 on the front and then blew up on the back.","index":155,"end_time":844.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":841.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It doesn''t matter.","index":156,"end_time":846.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":846.06,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s all about the front.","index":157,"end_time":847.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":846.78,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The front and a couple beers.","index":158,"end_time":850.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":849.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There you go.","index":159,"end_time":851.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":850.86,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":160,"end_time":853.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":852.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I can''t find this thing on the website, but I will when I do.","index":161,"end_time":856.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":853.14,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It was just a quote that was said which is something like luxury at a, at a lower price or something like that that I think we need to just remove or change it a little.","index":162,"end_time":867.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":856.66,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But I, I''ll look into that and I''ll get that over to you as well.","index":163,"end_time":869.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":867.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Otherwise, in terms of HubSpot and Erical, everything seems to be working pretty good.","index":164,"end_time":876.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":871.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Touch wood, everyone.","index":165,"end_time":879.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":878.03,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But yeah, I think, I think we''re good on our end.","index":166,"end_time":884.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":880.75,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What was the language you''re looking for on the website?","index":167,"end_time":887.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":885.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Something about like luxury at a discount or luxury at a lower price.","index":168,"end_time":892.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":888.55,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Something like that.","index":169,"end_time":892.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":892.03,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And if it''s luxury, it shouldn''t be at a lower price.","index":170,"end_time":897.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":894.63,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"See if I can run a site wide search real quick.","index":171,"end_time":906.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":903.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"In terms of all the changes with the website.","index":172,"end_time":923.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":921.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You guys have done everything all right?","index":173,"end_time":924.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":923.04,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yep.","index":174,"end_time":926,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":925.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":175,"end_time":927.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":926.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Cool.","index":176,"end_time":931.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":930.64,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''ll keep looking.","index":177,"end_time":932.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":932.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I can''t find it on a quick search.","index":178,"end_time":934.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":932.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":179,"end_time":936.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":935.68,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, other than that I don''t really have anything else for you guys.","index":180,"end_time":941.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":938.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean everybody, everything seems to be working fine.","index":181,"end_time":943.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":941.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh, actually for SMS marketing, based off of the number of like leads that we want to reach out to and the number of members that we have, do you guys have like a number that you, that you suspect that we''re going to send out in terms of like number of messages?","index":182,"end_time":965.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":947.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No, not off the top of my head.","index":183,"end_time":973.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":971.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I mean it would want to be basically leads coming in.","index":184,"end_time":976.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":973.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You would send them in addition to like the phone calls you''re making, right?","index":185,"end_time":980.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":977.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":186,"end_time":981.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":980.67,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You''re getting a few hundred leads, you know, a month.","index":187,"end_time":984.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":981.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":188,"end_time":985.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":984.99,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"How many texts are you looking to send them?","index":189,"end_time":987.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":985.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, it''s.","index":190,"end_time":988.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":987.87,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well that''s could be like one to three each.","index":191,"end_time":992.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":989.15,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, exactly.","index":192,"end_time":994.57,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":993.45,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But then it''s also, it''s not only the new leads, it''s also like any prior lead as well.","index":193,"end_time":999.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":994.57,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":194,"end_time":1000.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":999.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"In our pipeline members, probably about one or two times a month.","index":195,"end_time":1005.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1001.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Then you have past due text messages.","index":196,"end_time":1008.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1006.01,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So that can be at like a higher rate too.","index":197,"end_time":1011.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1008.33,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, I, I had calculated something like 25, 000 messages, but I wanted to kind of like ask you guys what you''re on.","index":198,"end_time":1019.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1011.61,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Your pitch in on that stuff too.","index":199,"end_time":1020.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1019.21,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, I think 25,000 might be on the high end, but it''s probably not super unrealistic.","index":200,"end_time":1030.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1022.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"SMS marketing is just costly, as I''m sure you found in your research.","index":201,"end_time":1034.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1031.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":202,"end_time":1036.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1036,"speaker_name":"Robert"},{"text":"No matter what provider you go through.","index":203,"end_time":1038,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1036.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":204,"end_time":1039.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1038.64,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, HubSpot is not horrible.","index":205,"end_time":1041.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1039.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It comes out to like less than a thousand dollars a month, but it''s also dependent on how many messages we''re sending out.","index":206,"end_time":1050.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1041.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":207,"end_time":1051.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1050.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you know what we could do and if you want us to join a call with the rep, you know, we can do that as usual.","index":208,"end_time":1057.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1051.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But I would recommend.","index":209,"end_time":1059.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1057.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, first we''ll talk to them and see what they can offer, see if they''ll kick in any discount or anything for us to try it out.","index":210,"end_time":1065.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1061.209,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But maybe pick one or two of like the segments we were just talking about.","index":211,"end_time":1070.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1065.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So like whether it''s new leads and, you know, stale leads or something, and then we have like one or two messages in a sequence and we just see how that goes.","index":212,"end_time":1079.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1070.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If it''s delivering ROI immediately, obviously it justifies.","index":213,"end_time":1082.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1079.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, let''s upgrade and send all these texts that we''re talking about.","index":214,"end_time":1085.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1083,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But I think that might be a good test.","index":215,"end_time":1087.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1085.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, how would we measure the ROI there?","index":216,"end_time":1091.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1088.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s just whether people are responding.","index":217,"end_time":1094.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1091.68,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":218,"end_time":1094.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1094.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, so it depend on.","index":219,"end_time":1096.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1094.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So if we start out with like a new lead segment and we see that they''re responding to text and not answering the phone, and then their membership changes to active or something like that, you know, we''re seeing me roi.","index":220,"end_time":1107.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1096.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Same thing with, you know, stale leads.","index":221,"end_time":1111.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1108.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Or if you''re seeing.","index":222,"end_time":1112.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1111.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If we do past due as a segment and you''re seeing people actually make their payments.","index":223,"end_time":1118.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1112.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Right.","index":224,"end_time":1119.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1119.14,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I know.","index":225,"end_time":1119.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1119.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m much more inclined to make a payment.","index":226,"end_time":1121.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1119.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m not going to pick up the phone when my gym''s calling me, but if they send me a text like, hey, it''s past due, be like, cool, click this link and buy it or, you know.","index":227,"end_time":1128.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1121.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, okay.","index":228,"end_time":1129.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1128.82,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":229,"end_time":1132.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1131.86,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s a good idea.","index":230,"end_time":1132.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1132.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I, I spoke to him and he said there was no trials for it, but.","index":231,"end_time":1135.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1132.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then you''re also locked into a year contract.","index":232,"end_time":1139.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1137.3,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":233,"end_time":1140.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1139.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":234,"end_time":1141.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1141.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I used to go to a powerhouse gym when I was in college.","index":235,"end_time":1144.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1142.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh yeah?","index":236,"end_time":1145.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1144.82,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":237,"end_time":1146.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1145.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Which one?","index":238,"end_time":1147.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1146.66,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It was in Salisbury, Maryland.","index":239,"end_time":1149.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1147.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s not 40, 000 square feet like you guys have, but okay.","index":240,"end_time":1153.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1149.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It was nice.","index":241,"end_time":1154.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1153.1,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":242,"end_time":1154.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1154.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It wasn''t bad.","index":243,"end_time":1155.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1154.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I switched to another one.","index":244,"end_time":1156.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1155.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I can''t remember the name, but that one was huge.","index":245,"end_time":1162.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1157.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Where are you at now?","index":246,"end_time":1164.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1163.63,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"My basement.","index":247,"end_time":1167.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1166.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, fair enough.","index":248,"end_time":1171.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1168.51,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s tough to get a workout in with a 10 month old.","index":249,"end_time":1175.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1171.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, that''s an excuse.","index":250,"end_time":1177.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1175.55,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, I know.","index":251,"end_time":1178.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1178.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I.","index":252,"end_time":1179.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1178.95,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"My buddy just asked me to be a groomsman''s wedding.","index":253,"end_time":1182.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1180.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m like, I gotta get in shape before I throw a suit on, man.","index":254,"end_time":1184.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1182.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There you go.","index":255,"end_time":1186,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1185.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"There you go.","index":256,"end_time":1186.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1186.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Especially if you got to do the speech.","index":257,"end_time":1189.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1187.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I don''t think I''m the best man.","index":258,"end_time":1190.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1189.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m just a groomsman, so.","index":259,"end_time":1192.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1190.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Just a man.","index":260,"end_time":1193.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1192.64,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, just a man.","index":261,"end_time":1194.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1193.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Fair enough.","index":262,"end_time":1196.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1196.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All right, cool.","index":263,"end_time":1199.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1198.32,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, what I''ll do is I''ll reach out to the rep again, see if we can get some kind of trial.","index":264,"end_time":1204.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1199.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"If he says no, then we''ll have another discussion and we''ll dive a little deeper into how many we really think we''re going to need to send out it to be effective and then do a little analysis there.","index":265,"end_time":1217.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1204.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":266,"end_time":1218.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1217.9,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, sounds good to me.","index":267,"end_time":1220.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1218.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Cool.","index":268,"end_time":1221.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1220.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":269,"end_time":1221.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1221.26,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"How many hours do we have left with you guys?","index":270,"end_time":1223.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1221.7,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean, we''re set up through June.","index":271,"end_time":1226.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1224.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":272,"end_time":1228.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1227.82,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we''ve got things we can do if you need help writing emails or putting any new sequences together.","index":273,"end_time":1236.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1229.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, there''s a lot of other things we can do in HubSpot since the system seems to be flowing pretty smoothly.","index":274,"end_time":1242.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1237.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, what do we think we can add?","index":275,"end_time":1247.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1242.83,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean, email campaigns are always good.","index":276,"end_time":1251.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1249.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I also think the website is just prime for.","index":277,"end_time":1254.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1251.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Especially as you guys are about to go into New Year''s resolution season.","index":278,"end_time":1258.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1254.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We could design also some social posts for you guys to put out.","index":279,"end_time":1262.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1258.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, it''s.","index":280,"end_time":1263.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1262.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s an hourly creative contract, so we can do anything that you guys want within the hours.","index":281,"end_time":1266.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1263.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":282,"end_time":1267.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1267.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All right, cool.","index":283,"end_time":1268.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1268.14,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":284,"end_time":1270.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1269.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, Robert and I will discuss offline and then we''ll come back to you guys.","index":285,"end_time":1273.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1270.02,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":286,"end_time":1274.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1273.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Cool.","index":287,"end_time":1276.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1275.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Thank you, guys.","index":288,"end_time":1276.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1276.18,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All right, see you.","index":289,"end_time":1277.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1277.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":290,"end_time":1278.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1278.14,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"}],"dateString":"2025-12-03T16:00:00.000Z","host_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86061042503?pwd=x0TBEgRs7qFmrRIEItauCzbH71kaq8.1","participants":["yefei@yhatinvest.com,alex.white@yhatinvest.com,tatiana@powerhousegymsoflo.com,wyattc@yhatinvest.com,robert.rudder@powerhousesoflo.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,tatiana.fernandez@powerhousesoflo.com,milan.wagner@powerhousesoflo.com,nina.belina@marketersindemand.com,cristina@pgmia.com,milan@pgmia.com","yefei@yhatinvest.com","alex.white@yhatinvest.com","tatiana@powerhousegymsoflo.com","wyattc@yhatinvest.com","robert.rudder@powerhousesoflo.com","tatiana.fernandez@powerhousesoflo.com","milan.wagner@powerhousesoflo.com","nina.belina@marketersindemand.com","cristina@pgmia.com","milan@pgmia.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KB35HD2DB1VKXJ12JTM0CRX6","organizer_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.9,"bullets":["Resolved HubSpot–AirCall contact sync issue; Milan confirmed the system is now functioning properly.","Identified overdue HubSpot invoice; Milan acknowledged and will follow up to resolve.","Proposed phased SMS campaign pilot to measure ROI before full-scale rollout.","Suggested utilizing open contract hours for year-end email campaigns and social media creatives.","Colin offered design support for updated web content and New Year marketing materials."],"highlights":[{"quote":"Otherwise, in terms of HubSpot and AirCall, everything seems to be working pretty good.","speaker":"Milan Wagner"},{"quote":"We could design also some social posts for you guys to put out.","speaker":"Colin Costigan"},{"quote":"We had a really good month in November, our best month of the year.","speaker":"Robert"}],"topics":["delivery","marketing","billing","website"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-1106-preview","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-12-03T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Sales Performance and Lead Management**\n\nThe team is seeing positive momentum with a strong sales month in November, signaling a promising holiday season.\n\n- **November marked the best sales month of the year**, indicating customers are starting holiday shopping early, according to Robert (06:25)  \n    - This uptick suggests the sales pipeline is active and ready for end-of-year campaigns  \n    - Robert’s optimism sets a positive baseline for forecasting December performance  \n    - Maintaining this momentum requires close monitoring of lead flow and conversion rates  \n    - This context justifies ramping up outreach efforts and marketing support for the holiday period\n\n- **Lead management system issues with HubSpot and Air Call were resolved**, ensuring sales contacts and calls sync properly, Milan confirmed (08:31)  \n    - Earlier problems caused duplicate or incomplete contact records, impacting follow-up accuracy  \n    - Fixing this restores sales team efficiency and data quality for pipeline tracking  \n    - Milan emphasized team adjustment to new systems is ongoing, highlighting training needs  \n    - Resolving these sync issues reduces risk of lost leads and missed sales opportunities\n\n## **Website Content and Messaging Updates**\n\nImmediate website content fixes are planned to better reflect the brand’s positioning and improve customer engagement.\n\n- **A video on the website needs replacing with an updated tour video from the content team**, Milan committed to deliver it soon (10:03)  \n    - Colin and Nina confirmed they have access to Squarespace but await the new video file  \n    - Updating the video will better showcase the facility and enhance visitor conversion  \n    - This content refresh supports the upcoming New Year’s resolution marketing push  \n    - Timely video replacement is vital to keep the site fresh and competitive\n\n- **The phrase “luxury at a lower price” on the site will be removed or reworded** to align with brand integrity, Milan noted (14:12)  \n    - Milan suggested luxury messaging should not imply discounting, to maintain premium appeal  \n    - Colin committed to searching the site and making necessary edits quickly  \n    - Clear, consistent messaging is key to differentiating from competitors  \n    - Adjusting this language supports the brand’s long-term positioning strategy\n\n## **SMS Marketing Strategy and Cost Management**\n\nThe team is planning a targeted SMS campaign to boost engagement, balancing message volume with budget constraints.\n\n- **Estimated SMS volume could reach about 25,000 messages per month**, covering new leads, existing pipeline, and past due reminders, Milan explained (16:11)  \n    - Colin noted this number is on the high end but plausible given lead flow and member base  \n    - HubSpot’s SMS pricing approximates under **$1,000 per month**, depending on volume (17:18)  \n    - Milan will reconnect with the SMS vendor rep to explore trial options or discounts (19:56)  \n    - Testing limited segments first will help measure ROI before full rollout\n\n- **ROI measurement will focus on response rates and membership activation or payment completion**, Colin outlined (18:08)  \n    - Text responses converting to active memberships or payments will demonstrate campaign success  \n    - Prioritizing past due payment reminders via SMS may yield immediate revenue impact  \n    - This approach reduces wasted spend and informs future scaling decisions  \n    - Milan plans to analyze message effectiveness with the team before final commitments\n\n## **Contract Status and Service Availability**\n\nThe team confirmed ongoing support and service availability through mid-year, ensuring continuity for upcoming initiatives.\n\n- **Existing service contract with Colin’s team is active through June**, Colin confirmed (20:24)  \n    - This provides a runway for additional HubSpot work, including email campaigns and sequences  \n    - The team can deploy creative support such as social media posts aligned with seasonal promotions  \n    - This flexibility allows for adaptive marketing tactics based on sales trends and customer feedback  \n    - Robert and Milan will discuss internal priorities and return with requests to Colin’s team\n\n- **Past due HubSpot invoice from November 29 was identified and acknowledged**, Milan committed to addressing it promptly (11:23)  \n    - Timely payment will prevent service disruptions during critical marketing periods  \n    - This highlights the need for routine billing oversight to avoid operational hiccups  \n    - Colin flagged this proactively to maintain smooth platform access  \n    - Resolving it ensures uninterrupted use of essential CRM and marketing tools","outline":null,"keywords":["HubSpot","Air Call","SMS marketing","website updates","lead management","holiday sales"],"overview":"- **Strong Sales Forecast:** November had best sales month of the year, indicating strong holiday shopping momentum.  \n- **Lead Management Fixes:** HubSpot and Air Call issues resolved, improving contact syncing and sales team efficiency.  \n- **Website Content Updates:** New tour video needed for website; current content must better reflect brand integrity.  \n- **SMS Campaign Plans:** Targeted SMS campaign may send 25,000 messages monthly, costing under $1,000; ROI focused on membership activation.  \n- **Contract and Service Continuity:** Service contract active through June; creative marketing support available for ongoing campaigns.  \n- **Invoice Acknowledgement:** Past due HubSpot invoice needs prompt action to prevent service disruption during busy marketing periods.","action_items":"\n**Milan Wagner**\nNotify team that routing call info without data input must be manual due to sync limitations (09:52)\nObtain updated tour video from content team and send for website update (10:45)\nAddress past due HubSpot invoice from November 29 (11:30)\nLocate and revise/remove ''luxury at a lower price'' phrase on website (14:13)\nReach out to SMS marketing rep to request trial or negotiate terms (19:56)\nDiscuss SMS marketing strategy and message volume with Robert before follow-up with marketers (21:07)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nSwap out website video promptly once received from Milan (11:05)\nAssist with SMS marketing rep engagement or join call for negotiation if needed (17:30)\nSupport email campaigns, new sequences, social media posts, and website enhancements as needed within contract hours through June (20:21)\n\n**Robert Rudder**\nCoordinate offline discussion with Milan regarding SMS marketing volume and strategy (21:07)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"4ca61c59-da71-4eec-a8d0-6d20572e59dc","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
