-- Meeting: New North x Sedra Solutions: Weekly Meeting (2025-11-26 16:30:00+00)
WITH new_meeting AS (
  INSERT INTO compass_meetings (contract_id, meeting_date, source, external_id, title, participants, duration_seconds, recording_url, transcript, sentiment, raw_metadata, created_at, updated_at)
  VALUES (
    '292bf658-a285-4fdd-a6e5-d352a30347c9',
    '2025-11-26 16:30:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01KAVDEZVDFJH6PCAHSQJSY42N',
    'New North x Sedra Solutions: Weekly Meeting',
    '{"Taylor Doerbaum","Jackie Wheeler","fahad al mutawa"}'::text[],
    905,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/88927304763?pwd=asbbQolEtVpMuYX5uccJpOibhnlog1.1',
    '{"id":"01KAVDEZVDFJH6PCAHSQJSY42N","title":"New North x Sedra Solutions: Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **End-of-Year Sales and Marketing Strategy**\n\nThe team agreed to focus on a targeted campaign to encourage paid proof of concepts (POCs) before the end of the year to capture leftover IT budgets.\n\n- **Jackie Wheeler proposed a campaign targeting prospects with leftover IT budgets to start paid POCs before December 31st** to use their remaining funds and test Cedra’s platform in advance of 2026 planning (00:48)  \n    - Taylor Doerbaum emphasized creating a specific audience list to efficiently reach interested contacts through Lemlist or LinkedIn, as broad campaigns would be too large to complete this month  \n    - Fahad al Mutawa stressed the necessity of targeting qualified leads only to avoid wasted resources on non-revenue prospects, and agreed paid POCs must have clear limits like **20,000 transactions max**  \n    - Jackie clarified the message should focus on a low-risk, paid trial to show time savings and platform value, not free trials, to ensure revenue generation and quality leads  \n\n- **Taylor Doerbaum updated that ABM email campaigns will be restructured next week to accommodate new messaging and domain scaling, pausing current sequences to save resources** (02:45)  \n    - The team plans to relaunch with clearer calls to action like scheduling demos starting January, aligning with the end-of-year messaging push  \n    - Jackie suggested LinkedIn posts as a low-effort alternative to email for broader reach but recognized email’s benefit for targeted outreach to known prospects  \n\n## **Pricing and High-Profile Sales Opportunity**\n\nThe finalized pricing model is set, and Fahad shared a promising lead with a major bankruptcy case that could become a flagship client and marketing asset.\n\n- **Fahad confirmed the pricing model is finalized and has been delivered to Weil, while revealing ongoing talks with the Mint Group for a multi-billion-dollar bankruptcy case** involving alleged **$2 billion embezzlement** and **$10 billion in debt** (04:57)  \n    - Fahad described how this case could serve as a powerful case study and marketing tool, given its high profile and media coverage  \n    - The Mint Group requested a joint webinar in early January to showcase the platform, positioning Cedra for significant exposure among major banks and legal players  \n    - Fahad is offering the Mint Group a near-cost deal to secure the case, viewing it as an investment in brand recognition and market positioning  \n\n- **Jackie and Fahad discussed discount offers, agreeing discounts for beta testers of the AI Investment Investigator product are separate from POC campaigns** (08:32)  \n    - Fahad emphasized selective offer application to avoid free work for low-potential clients, reinforcing that public campaigns must be carefully targeted to protect resources  \n\n## **Marketing and Advertising Updates**\n\nThe marketing team is shifting budget focus to LinkedIn ads and finalizing creative assets to support upcoming campaigns.\n\n- **Taylor reported completion of new ad creative for the demo landing page, reallocating budget from Google Ads to LinkedIn based on better performance metrics** (13:12)  \n    - Google Ads will now be limited to branded campaigns only to conserve budget  \n    - The new LinkedIn campaign, including images and ad copy, is ready and will launch after Fahad’s approval for maximum impact  \n\n- **Content scheduling is underway with all main page posts loaded in Publer, and Fahad’s post designs are being finalized based on documents he provided**  \n    - The procurement video animation is being adjusted to feature Cedra at the center with spokes, with graphics work ongoing and expected completion soon  \n\n## **Lead Research and Targeting**\n\nFahad is preparing research to identify and prioritize law firms and individuals for targeted outreach beyond the Mint Group connection.\n\n- **Fahad will send a press release and additional research to Taylor and Jackie to help pinpoint relevant contacts and firms to target for the Mint Group-related opportunity and other prospects** (14:10)  \n    - This research aims to refine the audience for outreach, ensuring campaigns focus on high-potential leads familiar with Cedra’s brand  \n    - Taylor highlighted the value of this targeted approach to increase campaign efficiency and engagement rates  \n\n## **Process and Workflow Adjustments**\n\nThe team is optimizing campaign management to allow message updates without disrupting ongoing outreach efforts.\n\n- **Taylor explained that Lemlist requires pausing current email sequences to update messages, so the plan is to launch new campaigns with refreshed content and pause existing sequences to avoid wasted sends** (02:45)  \n    - This approach includes potentially purchasing more domains to increase sending capacity and avoid bottlenecks  \n    - The team will restart outreach with new messaging in January after the year-end POC push, maintaining momentum without overlap or fatigue  \n\n## **Strategic Positioning and Vision**\n\nFahad and Jackie underscored the importance of focusing on high-value, targeted engagements rather than broad, untargeted campaigns to maximize ROI and build strategic partnerships.\n\n- **Fahad stressed that deals like the Mint Group’s case put Cedra “on the map” and represent the type of high-profile exposure needed to scale efficiently** (06:34)  \n    - He sees selective paid POCs and beta programs as strategic tools to build credibility and market presence without diluting resources  \n    - Jackie reinforced that messaging must clearly communicate value and urgency around IT budget timing to convert interested prospects into paying customers before year-end (09:57)","outline":null,"keywords":["Year-end budget","Proof of Concept","ABM campaigns","bankruptcy case","LinkedIn outreach","paid POC"],"overview":"- **End-of-Year Strategy:** Focus on targeted paid POCs to utilize leftover IT budgets before December 31st.  \n- **Audience Targeting:** Create a specific list for outreach; avoid broad campaigns to efficiently reach interested contacts.  \n- **Finalized Pricing Model:** Pricing delivered to Weil, with ongoing talks for a high-profile bankruptcy case worth $10 billion in debt.  \n- **Marketing Focus Shift:** Budget moving to LinkedIn ads; new ad creative ready to launch after video approval.  \n- **Lead Research Enhancement:** Press release and research to identify targeted law firms and individuals for outreach.  \n- **Optimizing Campaign Management:** New messages to be launched in January; existing sequences will pause to prevent overlap.","action_items":"\n**Taylor Doerbaum**\nCreate a targeted audience segment in Lemlist for the year-end POC campaign and prepare to launch in December (01:50)\nPause existing ABM email sequences and prepare new campaigns with updated messaging to launch next week (02:45)\nSend updated procurement video animation for review once graphics complete (12:15)\nShare new LinkedIn and Google ad creative packages with team for approval before going live (12:15)\n\n**Jackie Wheeler**\nRefine messaging for paid POC campaign targeting leftover IT budgets, considering simple LinkedIn posts versus focused email campaigns (11:59)\nContinue ideation on pitch encouraging prospects to do POC to use IT budget and prepare messaging for early next week discussion (11:59)\n\n**Fahad Al Mutawa**\nShare press release and research on Mint Group bankruptcy case and related target law firms to aid campaign targeting strategy (14:10)\nMonitor ongoing discussions and feedback from Mint Group and coordinate webinar plans for early January (05:45)\n"},"duration":15.09000015258789,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"id":1,"name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"id":2,"name":"fahad al mutawa"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hi.","index":0,"end_time":1.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Hi.","index":1,"end_time":3.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Good morning.","index":2,"end_time":3.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Good morning.","index":3,"end_time":4.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":4,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Happy almost Thanksgiving.","index":4,"end_time":6.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":5.28,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I know, it''s so close.","index":5,"end_time":8.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":7.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Hello.","index":6,"end_time":11.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":11.2,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Hello.","index":7,"end_time":12.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":12.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"How are you guys?","index":8,"end_time":14.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":13.6,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"How are you doing?","index":9,"end_time":16.319,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":15.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"How''s your week been?","index":10,"end_time":17.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":16.319,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Good, Good, been good.","index":11,"end_time":20.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":17.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Staying busy.","index":12,"end_time":20.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":20.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s slowing down.","index":13,"end_time":23.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":22.32,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"As you guys could imagine.","index":14,"end_time":25.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":24,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Nobody''s responding to any emails or taking any meetings after today.","index":15,"end_time":29.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":25.6,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yes, yes.","index":16,"end_time":31.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":29.94,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So many of my clients have been saying the same thing.","index":17,"end_time":32.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":31.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s like just after Thanksgiving, people are like, the year doesn''t exist anymore.","index":18,"end_time":36.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":32.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s funny, but, yeah, we tend to see a lot of slowdown in that time of year.","index":19,"end_time":43.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":37.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s expected.","index":20,"end_time":45.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":43.86,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yes, it''s expected.","index":21,"end_time":47.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":46.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"One thing I was thinking about is maybe it''s worth pushing out an email campaign that talks about get a POC in before the end of the year, use up your budget kind of thing.","index":22,"end_time":61.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":48.74,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Like when people have it budget that they got to spend before the end of the year.","index":23,"end_time":64.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":61.73,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Like, maybe this is the perfect time to do a poc.","index":24,"end_time":66.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":64.69,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Something like that.","index":25,"end_time":67.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":67.01,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Maybe.","index":26,"end_time":68.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":67.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Maybe that would resonate with people.","index":27,"end_time":69.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":68.41,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":28,"end_time":73.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":73.09,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":29,"end_time":74.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":74.37,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Is it with the, like the current.","index":30,"end_time":76.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":75.41,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The current list we run now, or is this a specific group?","index":31,"end_time":80.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":77.09,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, no, it would work together.","index":32,"end_time":81.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":80.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Ideally it would be with people who we think might have interest and would probably want to do a POC before they become a customer.","index":33,"end_time":88.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":82.42,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So, you know, it''s like, you know, get in a poc, pay for the POC now, you know, kind of thing, use up your budget, get.","index":34,"end_time":96.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":89.78,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Get a foot in the door.","index":35,"end_time":97.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":96.42,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Kind of get started with.","index":36,"end_time":98.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":97.54,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"With seeing what Cedra can do for you in the new year.","index":37,"end_time":101.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":98.94,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But you''ve got it budget to spend.","index":38,"end_time":104.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":102.58,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Let''s, you know, this is the perfect time to set up a POC with us and see what we can do for you in the new year.","index":39,"end_time":109.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":104.62,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Something like that.","index":40,"end_time":110.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":109.3,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":41,"end_time":111.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":110.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, I would recommend if we want to fit that into the last month.","index":42,"end_time":114.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":111.33,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Here is.","index":43,"end_time":115.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":114.65,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Create a specific audience for that.","index":44,"end_time":117.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":115.85,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know right now we have so many running with thousands of contacts, so it just wouldn''t get through that many.","index":45,"end_time":122.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":117.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But if there''s like a specific group that you''re like, this would be a good clientele for this, then we can create a new campaign group within Lemlist and we could launch that next week.","index":46,"end_time":133.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":122.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that way we can start getting those out within December.","index":47,"end_time":136.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":133.09,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But with the current amount of lists we have running, we would just never get through it by the end of the month.","index":48,"end_time":141.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":137.05,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But if you have one, then we could.","index":49,"end_time":143.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":141.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"What we could do.","index":50,"end_time":144.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":143.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So one of the updates I have too is for the.","index":51,"end_time":147.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":144.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Let me pull this up.","index":52,"end_time":150.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":149.05,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I was just thinking maybe not an email campaign, actually.","index":53,"end_time":152.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":150.13,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Maybe it could be just a LinkedIn post.","index":54,"end_time":154.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":152.37,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It could be something as oh yeah, because that way that reaches the maximum amount of people immediately and has no lift.","index":55,"end_time":162.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":154.05,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So.","index":56,"end_time":163.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":162.73,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, either way.","index":57,"end_time":166.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":165.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And if it''s one email, it''s much easier to get through a sequence than if it''s like several emails with follow up, follow up after.","index":58,"end_time":173.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":166.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So if it''s just one singular email that we want to send out, we could still utilize that through lemlist.","index":59,"end_time":178.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":173.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"What I was going to share, I''ll just skip to this.","index":60,"end_time":181.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":179.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Here is for the ABM campaigns, now that we have that updated sequence with.","index":61,"end_time":188.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":181.14,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The way the email platform works with lemlist is you have to pause everything in order to change any kind of emails.","index":62,"end_time":196.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":188.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And so instead of doing that for all of these, we''re going to create new SE or new campaigns with the separate groups and kind of lump them together.","index":63,"end_time":203.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":196.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because right now we have so many individual ones and try to push through more, potentially purchasing more domains too, so we can get through the lists which will help with that.","index":64,"end_time":213.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":203.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So next week we''re going to be launching that.","index":65,"end_time":215.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":213.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It doesn''t make sense to do it right now, obviously at the end of this week.","index":66,"end_time":219.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":215.95,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we''re going to do that next week and we would, we would pause all the existing ones and restart now the new messaging.","index":67,"end_time":226.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":219.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s clear.","index":68,"end_time":227.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":226.49,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"More to the point, schedule a demo because we don''t want to waste any more time or resources with lemlist pushing out the emails that we''ve already changed.","index":69,"end_time":234.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":227.25,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So if you wanted, we could pause even those updated emails and just start with what you''re saying where we focus on the end of the year messaging and then we could pick back up in January with the new updated emails if you want.","index":70,"end_time":249.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":234.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"If you''re saying that this is like a good thing, that people would be like, oh yeah, it''s the end of the year, I can XYZ people are.","index":71,"end_time":255.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":249.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Doing their 2026 planning already.","index":72,"end_time":257.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":255.52,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"They''re doing their, their financial planning and everything and they''re figuring out their budgets for.","index":73,"end_time":262.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":257.28,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I mean, maybe it''s even too late for that.","index":74,"end_time":264.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":262.88,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Honestly, some people might have already finished that up already, but if they have any IT budget left to spend this year, this is the perfect time to do it to sign up for a poc.","index":75,"end_time":274.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":264.92,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But this also ties into your status update here at the bottom of the slide, the offer.","index":76,"end_time":279.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":275.6,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Fahad, have you had any further thoughts on the pricing and an offer?","index":77,"end_time":284.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":280.24,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"No, that''s fine, that''s fine.","index":78,"end_time":295.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":292.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I just wanted to check and see.","index":79,"end_time":296.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":295.08,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"We did finish our pricing model.","index":80,"end_time":299.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":297.92,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It''s set to Go.","index":81,"end_time":301.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":300.08,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"We already gave it to Weil.","index":82,"end_time":303.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":301.2,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I had a meeting earlier today with the Mint Group who have a huge bankruptcy case out of New York that they want to utilize our solution for.","index":83,"end_time":311.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":303.62,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So hopefully.","index":84,"end_time":313.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":312.02,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Fingers crossed.","index":85,"end_time":313.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":313.3,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"This just happened a few hours ago.","index":86,"end_time":315.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":313.98,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":87,"end_time":316.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":316.02,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It''s a multi billion dollar bankruptcy.","index":88,"end_time":318.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":316.74,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"The CEO has been accused of embezzling funds out of the business.","index":89,"end_time":322.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":318.98,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It''s all over the news.","index":90,"end_time":324.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":323.14,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So it''s actually quite an interesting case.","index":91,"end_time":326.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":324.18,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Hopefully we''ll get feedback over the next few days because that would be an amazing, amazing.","index":92,"end_time":332.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":326.14,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Case study.","index":93,"end_time":334.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":333.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s a light case.","index":94,"end_time":337.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":334.86,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It''s all over the news.","index":95,"end_time":338.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":337.06,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Everybody knows about it.","index":96,"end_time":339.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":338.22,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"The guy''s been accused of, you know, embezzling $2 billion out of this business.","index":97,"end_time":343.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":339.5,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Oh, my goodness.","index":98,"end_time":345.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":344.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They have $10 billion in debt from major banks and everybody''s all over him.","index":99,"end_time":351.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":345.98,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"He spent $500,000 for a special chef and150,000 on some kind of.","index":100,"end_time":358.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":351.18,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"What was it called?","index":101,"end_time":359.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":358.79,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Exercise something.","index":102,"end_time":360.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":359.43,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Celebrity trainer.","index":103,"end_time":362.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":361.03,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"That''s all on company expense.","index":104,"end_time":365.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":364.39,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So you could imagine the shareholders are pissed off.","index":105,"end_time":369.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":365.99,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Now, I believe the Mint Group has been hired and the Mint Group wants to utilize our software for this.","index":106,"end_time":375.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":369.43,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Amazing.","index":107,"end_time":376.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":375.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They also want to do a webinar early January between us and them.","index":108,"end_time":382.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":377.11,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So I actually, I gave in.","index":109,"end_time":384.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":383.11,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I agreed to that because it came out of them.","index":110,"end_time":386.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":384.87,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"They requested it.","index":111,"end_time":387.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":386.71,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"But I''m hoping.","index":112,"end_time":391.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":390.24,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I''m hoping that we''ll get this deal.","index":113,"end_time":393.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":391.08,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It''s.","index":114,"end_time":394.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":393.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It just puts us on the map.","index":115,"end_time":395.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":394.16,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It''s what we''re looking for.","index":116,"end_time":396.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":395.48,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Totally.","index":117,"end_time":397.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":396.88,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"That is so exciting.","index":118,"end_time":399.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":397.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I mean, horrible, horrible situation.","index":119,"end_time":401.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":399.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Exciting for you.","index":120,"end_time":403.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":401.92,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":121,"end_time":403.839,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":403.44,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"If there wasn''t a horrible situation, we, we wouldn''t have a business.","index":122,"end_time":406.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":403.839,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"That''s true.","index":123,"end_time":408.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":407.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This is the reality.","index":124,"end_time":410.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":408.96,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"The things I think they can get away with, it''s so crazy.","index":125,"end_time":413.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":410.4,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"That''s what I''m thinking.","index":126,"end_time":415.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":414.24,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"A couple of million.","index":127,"end_time":416.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":415.52,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Nobody will figure it out.","index":128,"end_time":417.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":416.4,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Steal a couple of billion, you got another thing coming.","index":129,"end_time":420.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":417.56,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"That''s what I don''t understand about a couple of the stories you''ve told us.","index":130,"end_time":424.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":421.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I don''t understand how people think like, oh, yeah, I''m getting away with this one.","index":131,"end_time":428.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":425.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I. I will share.","index":132,"end_time":432.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":431.31,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I''ll share with you the press release that''s out on the case.","index":133,"end_time":435.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":432.51,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It''s.","index":134,"end_time":436.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":435.79,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It''s public.","index":135,"end_time":436.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":436.15,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It''s not a secret.","index":136,"end_time":437.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":436.55,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I''ll.","index":137,"end_time":437.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":437.31,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I''ll put it on slack after this meeting, okay?","index":138,"end_time":440.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":437.91,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It''s just, it''s interesting because.","index":139,"end_time":442.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":440.67,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It''s interesting because of the exposure we can potentially get out of major banks, out of major players, out of this investigation especially, we''re able to find where the 2 billion end up going.","index":140,"end_time":453.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":442.43,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yes.","index":141,"end_time":454.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":453.88,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"That''s going to be massive.","index":142,"end_time":456.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":454.92,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, to me that''s worth giving them a discount to get the case right more than promoting it on LinkedIn.","index":143,"end_time":466.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":457.8,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So I told them, I told them I want the case, I''m willing to do it at close to cost, just get us, because that''s the best kind of marketing you could ever pay for.","index":144,"end_time":476.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":466.6,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So I''m cautiously optimistic, as usual.","index":145,"end_time":481.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":478.48,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"But it''s looking good so far.","index":146,"end_time":483.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":481.56,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Let''s see what happens over the next few days.","index":147,"end_time":485.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":483.6,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"But regarding an offer, I don''t know if you have something in mind that you think you can message it out.","index":148,"end_time":491.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":486.4,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"You know, sign up for a POC, we''ll give you a 10% discount, 15% discount.","index":149,"end_time":498.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":492.16,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"But I don''t want to put a value because the discount is going to depend on what they actually, how much data they have.","index":150,"end_time":507.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":499.38,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Because their bill could be 20,000, but their bill could also be 200,000.","index":151,"end_time":512.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":507.54,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"No, I wasn''t thinking an offer with like, I wasn''t thinking a discount with the, with the poc.","index":152,"end_time":518.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":512.66,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I was thinking about just, you know, use up your IT spend before the end of the year because it''s.","index":153,"end_time":523.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":518.9,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Use it or lose it.","index":154,"end_time":523.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":523.02,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"With the, with the offer that we were talking about that was more around, we''re looking for five customers to be beta testers of our AI investment Investigator or something along those lines.","index":155,"end_time":532.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":523.94,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And those people would get like we give them some sort of deal if they are one of our early adopters.","index":156,"end_time":541.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":533.76,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So, you know, it''s that kind of like we''re, we''re looking for just a certain number of people to work with.","index":157,"end_time":546.999,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":542.08,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But maybe that doesn''t make sense either.","index":158,"end_time":548.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":546.999,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"What happens?","index":159,"end_time":550.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":549.28,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Let''s say we do something that says sign up by January 30 for the Sidra platform and we will give you X, Y and Z.","index":160,"end_time":561.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":550.32,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"But let''s say.","index":161,"end_time":563.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":562.2,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"And the first 10 people that sign up.","index":162,"end_time":565.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":563.32,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Right, but let''s say these 10 people are not even a potential customer or don''t even have potential revenue for the future.","index":163,"end_time":572.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":565.32,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Why are we investing, giving them something as a proof of concept?","index":164,"end_time":576.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":572.68,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I mean, somebody like Weil, I''m happy to do it for no cost.","index":165,"end_time":579.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":576.2,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"You know, I believe in what we have and I''m willing to give them a proof of concept.","index":166,"end_time":583.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":579.8,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"But when you publicly advertise it on LinkedIn, you might get a small shop somewhere that wants a free proof of concept.","index":167,"end_time":592.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":584.19,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"But with while I know will pay out long term, but with these guys, it will never pay out.","index":168,"end_time":597.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":592.99,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Okay, so I''m not talking about a free proof of concept, I''m talking about a paid Proof of concept.","index":169,"end_time":602.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":597.31,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Use up your IT budget like you''ve got another 10 grand to spend in your IT budget before the end of the year.","index":170,"end_time":608.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":602.43,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"This is the perfect time to do a proof of concept with Cedra.","index":171,"end_time":610.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":608.31,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"If you''re thinking ahead about how you''re going to set up, stay ahead of the game in 2026, how are you going to expand your business?","index":172,"end_time":617.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":610.75,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"How are you going to use your IT spend?","index":173,"end_time":620.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":617.33,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"The most effective way to make your business more efficient in a changing landscape?","index":174,"end_time":626.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":620.65,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Cedra is the answer.","index":175,"end_time":627.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":626.37,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Let''s do a POC before the end of the year or let''s get the ball rolling on a POC before the end of the year.","index":176,"end_time":632.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":627.41,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It''s that kind of messaging.","index":177,"end_time":634.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":632.93,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"If people have this leftover it spends that they''ve got to use up before December 31st.","index":178,"end_time":638.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":634.25,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So I''m just trying to think about ways that we could maybe tap into that to do a paid poc, not a free po.","index":179,"end_time":644.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":639.09,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ve never done a paid poc.","index":180,"end_time":647.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":645.85,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Most of them have been on our side.","index":181,"end_time":650.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":647.49,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So that''s why I always think in the gotcha.","index":182,"end_time":653.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":650.49,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"No, I''m thinking paid.","index":183,"end_time":654.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":653.09,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It''s a low risk way for them to use a budget.","index":184,"end_time":658.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":656.41,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"They already have to test out the platform to get a certain amount of data and we get a little bit of revenue from it.","index":185,"end_time":666.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":658.89,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I don''t mind if we can formulate it in a specific way, but has to be targeted.","index":186,"end_time":673.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":668.01,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It has to be with the right people.","index":187,"end_time":675.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":673.94,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"We have to have the opportunity to say, no, we can''t do it for you guys.","index":188,"end_time":678.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":675.62,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yes.","index":189,"end_time":679.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":678.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And it can''t be, here''s a billion records, upload them for me.","index":190,"end_time":683.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":679.86,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"No, no, it has to have.","index":191,"end_time":685.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":683.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, it has to be something, you know, reasonable.","index":192,"end_time":689.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":687.54,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":193,"end_time":690.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":690.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":194,"end_time":691.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":691.46,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"People.","index":195,"end_time":692.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":692.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And people understand that a proof of concept is never like, do a whole case for me.","index":196,"end_time":696.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":692.54,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It''s do us, you know, take a sample of data, try something, maybe even look at a case you already completed, upload that data.","index":197,"end_time":704.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":696.18,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But something that''s not within reason, 20,000 transactions max or something like that and see how much time you would have spent using Cedra versus what you actually spent on it.","index":198,"end_time":717.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":705.09,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Sure.","index":199,"end_time":717.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":717.49,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So I''ll ideate on that a little bit.","index":200,"end_time":721.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":719.49,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And like I said, it could be as simple as a LinkedIn post.","index":201,"end_time":724.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":721.77,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It doesn''t have to be an email campaign or anything like that.","index":202,"end_time":726.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":724.37,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It could be something really simple.","index":203,"end_time":728.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":726.85,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But I''m just trying to see if we can tap into.","index":204,"end_time":730.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":728.21,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Give us the money that''s left over in your IT budget before the end of the year.","index":205,"end_time":733.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":730.85,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"That''s what it comes down to.","index":206,"end_time":735.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":733.95,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":207,"end_time":737.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":735.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And if you had like a, like I said, a specific audience, you might be able to reach them better through an email campaign than you would on LinkedIn.","index":208,"end_time":744.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":737.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because they might not see it on LinkedIn because we''re still growing that presence.","index":209,"end_time":748.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":744.95,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So if you did have like a specific group of people, like a list of contacts, it would be more beneficial.","index":210,"end_time":753.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":748.63,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We could come up with like a catchy subject line where it would catch their attention like before the end of the year, you know, something that makes it more time sensitive.","index":211,"end_time":760.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":753.39,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Whereas, like a post on LinkedIn might be tougher to reach the audience that you''re talking about.","index":212,"end_time":765.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":761.04,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So there''s something else to think about there.","index":213,"end_time":767.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":765.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":214,"end_time":769.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":768.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":215,"end_time":770.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":769.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yeah, we can touch base on that next week too.","index":216,"end_time":772.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":770.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":217,"end_time":774.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":773.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":218,"end_time":775.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":775.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Just as far as additional updates.","index":219,"end_time":777.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":775.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The procurement video with just that change we had to make that you left, Jackie, where we''re doing like the frame out with Cedra in the middle and the spokes, we just had to send that back to graphics first and then we''ll pick up that animation.","index":220,"end_time":788.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":777.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I''ll send that to you.","index":221,"end_time":789.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":788.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They''re working on that today and tomorrow.","index":222,"end_time":791.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":789.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":223,"end_time":791.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":791.28,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yes.","index":224,"end_time":792.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":792.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I just want to update you there.","index":225,"end_time":794.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":792.94,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"All the main page posts are scheduled in Publer.","index":226,"end_time":796.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":794.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''re wrapping up the designs for Fahad''s posts With those we created some posts based on the documents you sent.","index":227,"end_time":802.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":796.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that was really great.","index":228,"end_time":803.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":802.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we''ll send those over to you when those are complete.","index":229,"end_time":806.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":803.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We already talked about abm and then as far as paid ads, we are wrapping up the new image ad Creative Package 2 for the demo landing page campaign that we''re going to do.","index":230,"end_time":816.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":807.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Now that we reallocating the budget from Google Ads into LinkedIn, we put together a whole document with ad copy and text and images that we will get launched as soon as we get your approval.","index":231,"end_time":828.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":817.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then also Google Ads, we''re only going to do that branded campaign now to save some money there and push it more towards LinkedIn where we''ve seen more success.","index":232,"end_time":835.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":829.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I will send both of those over to you before they go live.","index":233,"end_time":838.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":835.92,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But we''re wrapping those up now, so you should see those soon.","index":234,"end_time":841.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":838.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yeah, those are my only updates that I had for you.","index":235,"end_time":846.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":843.04,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I''m really excited about this new update, Fahad, that you have.","index":236,"end_time":850.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":846.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So let me, let me share it with you.","index":237,"end_time":853.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":850.88,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I mean, I was trying to see, to be honest, honest, if I was able to figure out which law firms, which individuals, maybe we could target them even, you know, outside the Minsk group.","index":238,"end_time":863.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":853.72,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So when mints, you know, suggest us, they know who we are to an extent, yes.","index":239,"end_time":869.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":863.5,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"That''s good.","index":240,"end_time":870.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":869.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I''m gonna send you any research I have over the next few hours.","index":241,"end_time":875.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":871.34,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I''ll start off with a press release just to give you guys an indication.","index":242,"end_time":879.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":876.78,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"And then we could take it from there, see what we could do.","index":243,"end_time":882.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":880.3,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":244,"end_time":883.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":883.17,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"That sounds awesome.","index":245,"end_time":884.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":883.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":246,"end_time":885.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":884.53,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Looking forward to hearing about it.","index":247,"end_time":886.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":885.05,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":248,"end_time":887.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":886.93,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"All right, thanks.","index":249,"end_time":888.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":887.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, have a happy Thanksgiving and faha.","index":250,"end_time":890.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":888.81,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Have a good rest of your week.","index":251,"end_time":891.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":890.73,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And you''re having a Thanksgiving celebration tonight, aren''t you?","index":252,"end_time":894.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":891.73,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Tonight.","index":253,"end_time":894.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":894.45,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I''m on my way.","index":254,"end_time":895.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":894.89,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Okay.","index":255,"end_time":896.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":895.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Have a great time.","index":256,"end_time":897.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":896.49,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Bye, guys.","index":257,"end_time":899.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":898.769,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"By.","index":258,"end_time":899.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":899.73,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"}],"dateString":"2025-11-26T16:30:00.000Z","host_email":"taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/88927304763?pwd=asbbQolEtVpMuYX5uccJpOibhnlog1.1","participants":["taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com,baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com,j.wheeler@sedrasolutions.com,i.hamshari@sedrasolutions.com,f.almutawa@sedrasolutions.com","baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com","j.wheeler@sedrasolutions.com","i.hamshari@sedrasolutions.com","f.almutawa@sedrasolutions.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KAVDEZVDFJH6PCAHSQJSY42N","organizer_email":"taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
